Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.83,中文,,0,0,0,,《生命清單》 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:39.75,中文,,0,0,0,,這套怎麼樣 挺好的\N{\r外文}-How's this? Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:41.75,中文,,0,0,0,,性感 我喜歡\N{\r外文}Sexy. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.50,中文,,0,0,0,,還是換一套吧\N{\r外文}I think I'm going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:52.33,中文,,0,0,0,,別吃沙拉了\N{\r外文}Stop eating the salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.29,中文,,0,0,0,,請進\N{\r外文}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:13.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我想來告訴你一下 大家陸續開始來了\N{\r外文}I wanted to let you know people are starting to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:15.16,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了 亞歷克斯來了嗎\N{\r外文}Great. Is Alex here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:18.54,中文,,0,0,0,,沒有 但她會帶她做的豆子沙拉來的\N{\r外文}Uh, no. But she is gonna be bringing her bean salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:21.04,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯一向按自己的時間來\N{\r外文}Ah. Alex is on Alex time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:23.79,中文,,0,0,0,,而且她那豆子沙拉不吃也罷\N{\r外文}...and there's never a good time for that bean salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:26.58,中文,,0,0,0,,但你猜怎麼著 今天就放過她吧\N{\r外文}But you know what? Let's... Let's give her a break today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:29.54,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽 你總會替她找借口 你知道吧\N{\r外文}Mom, you are always making excuses for her. You realize that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.04,中文,,0,0,0,,大概因為她是我最愛的孩子\N{\r外文}It's 'cause she's my favorite child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:33.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 真相終於浮出水面了\N{\r外文}-Okay, the truth finally comes out. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.16,中文,,0,0,0,,還好我是你最愛的兒子 對吧\N{\r外文}-Ouch! I'm still your favorite son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.62,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 當然\N{\r外文}Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.70,中文,,0,0,0,,"你們怎麼還沒結婚啊"\N{\r外文}"Why aren't you married yet?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.75,中文,,0,0,0,,"你怎麼在唱片店裏工作"\N{\r外文}"Why do you work in a record store?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.54,中文,,0,0,0,,"你為什麼放棄教書"\N{\r外文}"Why'd you give up teaching?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.12,中文,,0,0,0,,"你為什麼沒讀完大學"\N{\r外文}"Why didn't you finish college?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你為什麼沒讀完大學\N{\r外文}Why didn't you finish college?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我是個愛生活的人 我從生活中學習 對吧\N{\r外文}I'm a life guy. I learn by living, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:51.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你很喜歡我這一點\N{\r外文}You love that about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:53.50,中文,,0,0,0,,對 是的\N{\r外文}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:54.45,中文,,0,0,0,,對\N{\r外文}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.33,中文,,0,0,0,,哎 要不這樣\N{\r外文}Hey, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:00.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我們走進去 打個招呼\N{\r外文}What about we go in there, we say our hellos,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:03.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你給我個暗號 然後我們偷偷溜進你小時候的臥室\N{\r外文}and then you give me the high sign, we sneak off to your childhood bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.33,中文,,0,0,0,,在芭比和肯的包圍下親熱\N{\r外文}and make out surrounded by the Barbies and Kens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你別想靠近我的芭比娃娃 臭小子\N{\r外文}Mm, you're not getting anywhere near my Barbies, buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.00,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.66,中文,,0,0,0,,（歡迎寶貝）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:20.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我把這個拿去廚房 好的\N{\r外文}-I'm going to take this into the kitchen. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 盧卡斯 嘿 佐伊 嘿\N{\r外文}Hey, Lucas. Hey, Zoe. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.25,中文,,0,0,0,,迎嬰派對快樂\N{\r外文}Happy baby shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.83,中文,,0,0,0,,來了 看起來不錯啊 是啊 好大一盤豆子沙拉\N{\r外文}-There it is. Looks good. Yeah. Famous bean salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.75,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.54,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\r外文}Super good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:32.66,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷阿姨\N{\r外文}Auntie Allie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你們好呀\N{\r外文}Hi, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:38.45,中文,,0,0,0,,這個派對太無聊了 爸爸要之後才讓我們吃蛋糕\N{\r外文}This party is so boring, and Dad won't let us have cake until later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.54,中文,,0,0,0,,父母怎麼這樣啊 對吧\N{\r外文}What is it with parents, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.33,中文,,0,0,0,,要不來玩一下我們著名的尋寶遊戲\N{\r外文}How about one of our famous scavenger hunts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:47.62,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我想要六件 能在哈利或赫敏房間裏找到的東西\N{\r外文}Okay, I want six items that I could find in Harry or Hermione's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:51.83,中文,,0,0,0,,如果這樣東西能讓無聊的大人消失 就有加分\N{\r外文}And bonus points for anything that can be used to make boring adults disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.04,中文,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎\N{\r外文}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.58,中文,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\r外文}Oh, one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:58.45,中文,,0,0,0,,開始之前 你們要補充營養\N{\r外文}You guys need proper nutritional preparation before we commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:00.75,中文,,0,0,0,,好勒\N{\r外文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.25,中文,,0,0,0,,佐伊 介紹你認識茱莉亞 你好\N{\r外文}-Zoe, I want you to meet Julia. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 很高興認識你\N{\r外文}-Hi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.54,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 你好\N{\r外文}Alex! Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.29,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 凱莉 哇 天啊 看看你\N{\r外文}Oh, Kelly, wow. Oh my God, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.75,中文,,0,0,0,,別看 我肚子太大了\N{\r外文}No, don't. I'm so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.62,中文,,0,0,0,,可是也很美\N{\r外文}But so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.29,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 謝謝你啦\N{\r外文}Aw, why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.29,中文,,0,0,0,,聽說你不得不放棄了教書\N{\r外文}I heard you had to give up teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你現在為你母親工作 對\N{\r外文}-And you're working for your mother now? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.75,中文,,0,0,0,,然後你男朋友在唱片店工作\N{\r外文}And your boyfriend has a job at a record store?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我都不知道現在還有唱片店呢\N{\r外文}I didn't know there were record stores anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.66,中文,,0,0,0,,就剩下那一間了\N{\r外文}Uh-huh. There's one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:30.50,中文,,0,0,0,,工作的空餘時間 他在開發一款遊戲\N{\r外文}The rest of the time, he's developing a video game called
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.75,中文,,0,0,0,,要麼是《美國殭屍 血腥末日》 或者是《遊樂場末日》\N{\r外文}eitherAmerican Zombie: Blood Apocalypse orPlayground Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.75,中文,,0,0,0,,將來有一天 你會哭著喊著要你媽買給你的\N{\r外文}And one day, you'll make your mommy buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:40.25,中文,,0,0,0,,對啊 你會的\N{\r外文}Yes, you will. Yes, you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我得去找一下亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}I've got to go grab Alex for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:47.04,中文,,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白 趕緊和我朋友凱蒂認識一下\N{\r外文}Elizabeth, I am dying for you to meet my friend Katie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.12,中文,,0,0,0,,她是"羅斯美妝"的超級粉絲 來見見她 很快的\N{\r外文}She's a huge fan of Rose Cosmetics. Come meet her. Two seconds, two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天 謝天謝地你來了\N{\r外文}Oh my God. Thank God you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我以為我是唯一40歲以下 未懷孕或處於哺乳期的女人呢\N{\r外文}I thought I was the only woman under 40 not pregnant or lactating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 你好\N{\r外文}Hi. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.50,中文,,0,0,0,,令人難以忍受的賤人們 我恨她們所有人\N{\r外文}Insufferable bitches. I hate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.37,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 她們只是嫉妒 因為她們再也不能出去玩了\N{\r外文}Yeah. They're just jealous because they don't get out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:07.08,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 不過你也不出來玩了\N{\r外文}Yeah. Except you don't go out anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.95,中文,,0,0,0,,甚至都不回朋友電話了\N{\r外文}Or even call your friends back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你這是怎麼了啊\N{\r外文}What is going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.08,中文,,0,0,0,,有誰想吃軟糖嗎\N{\r外文}Anybody want a gummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.29,中文,,0,0,0,,有 能不能給我\N{\r外文}Yes. Can I have the, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.00,中文,,0,0,0,,五毫克 太棒了\N{\r外文}-They're five milligrams... Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.37,中文,,0,0,0,,乘以四 你應該沒問題的 棒極了\N{\r外文}-Times four. You should be good to go. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:21.16,中文,,0,0,0,,五小時後見 你不打算開車回家 對吧\N{\r外文}See you in five hours. You're not driving home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好 那就沒事 艾略特呢\N{\r外文}-Then you're fine. Where's Elliot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我們分手了 抱歉\N{\r外文}We broke up. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我得走了 嗯 不 沒事的\N{\r外文}-I gotta go. Yeah. No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我已經有兩個\N{\r外文}I've already gone on two--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你給孩子們吃蛋糕了嗎\N{\r外文}Did you give the kids cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.04,中文,,0,0,0,,額\N{\r外文}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.16,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\r外文}Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.00,中文,,0,0,0,,爽了\N{\r外文}Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.08,中文,,0,0,0,,是我幹的 必須的\N{\r外文}That was me. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.54,中文,,0,0,0,,朱利安 放鬆點吧 對不對 我們想說的是\N{\r外文}Julian, relax. I mean, right? Like, all we're saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.41,中文,,0,0,0,,就讓他們吃點蛋糕吧 多吃點\N{\r外文}-Let them eat cake. Lots of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.91,中文,,0,0,0,,能出什麼問題啊\N{\r外文}What could possibly go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我們去亞歷克斯阿姨的房間吧 也許她有鋼筆\N{\r外文}Let's go to Auntie Alex's room. Maybe she has a fountain pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,慢點 快點啊\N{\r外文}Slow down! Hurry up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.33,中文,,0,0,0,,芬恩 你的小雞雞真大\N{\r外文}Finn, you have a really big willy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.25,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\r外文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我被禁足了嗎 永遠\N{\r外文}-Am I grounded? Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:34.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我覺得朱利安永遠也不會原諒你了 你保證嗎\N{\r外文}-I don't think Julian'll ever forgive you. Is that a promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.50,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 嗨\N{\r外文}-Hi. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.29,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.45,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.95,中文,,0,0,0,,不過 說真的 你到底是怎麼了\N{\r外文}Seriously, though. What is going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.45,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼意思\N{\r外文}-What do you mean? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 我感覺或許你有點不知所措\N{\r外文}I don't know. I feel like maybe you're floundering a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:03.04,中文,,0,0,0,,感覺有點迷惘\N{\r外文}Feeling a little lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.08,中文,,0,0,0,,迷惘\N{\r外文}Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:08.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我交了個新男友 還有一份很棒的工作\N{\r外文}I have a new boyfriend and a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.00,中文,,0,0,0,,為自己母親工作\N{\r外文}Working for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.04,中文,,0,0,0,,向比你大一倍的女人推銷化妝品 簡直是個美夢啊\N{\r外文}Selling makeup to women twice your age? What a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.83,中文,,0,0,0,,沒錯 但這是工作嘛\N{\r外文}Yeah, but it's a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:21.58,中文,,0,0,0,,有前途 有保障 而且我越做越擅長了 對吧\N{\r外文}With a future and security, and a job I thought I was getting pretty good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.37,中文,,0,0,0,,對 你是挺擅長的\N{\r外文}Yeah, you're good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:28.04,中文,,0,0,0,,但這不是你 這不是讓你有激情的事\N{\r外文}It's not who you are. It's not what you're passionate about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.41,中文,,0,0,0,,激情被高估了 什麼\N{\r外文}-Passion is overrated. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:34.37,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 激情永遠持續不了多久 而且實在太累人了\N{\r外文}It is. It never lasts, and it's completely exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:38.25,中文,,0,0,0,,而且 我們這一代人不都這樣嗎\N{\r外文}Besides, isn't that what my generation is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:42.50,中文,,0,0,0,,降低期望值 放棄幼稚的夢想\N{\r外文}Lowering expectations and letting go of childish dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:46.45,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 你可不相信這話\N{\r外文}Alex, you do not believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.20,中文,,0,0,0,,再說了 我很喜歡為你工作 媽媽\N{\r外文}Besides, I love working for you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.00,中文,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\r外文}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:56.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你獨自一人建立了這家了不起的公司\N{\r外文}You built this incredible business all by yourself, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我想參與其中\N{\r外文}and I want to be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.41,中文,,0,0,0,,讓你驕傲\N{\r外文}And make you proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.62,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 既然你都這麼說了\N{\r外文}Well, since you put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.50,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\r外文}-Mom. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我有消息要宣佈\N{\r外文}I have some news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:13.87,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\r外文}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.91,中文,,0,0,0,,芬恩正式邀請我同居了\N{\r外文}Finn officially asked me to move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:21.83,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\r外文}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:25.70,中文,,0,0,0,,至少讓我住到找到新住處 這樣一來 我倆都能省點房租\N{\r外文}Well, at least until I find a new place. In the meantime, we both save on rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.91,中文,,0,0,0,,好浪漫啊\N{\r外文}How romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你們為什麼都討厭他\N{\r外文}Why do you guys all hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.91,中文,,0,0,0,,是因為他沒讀完大學嗎\N{\r外文}Is it because he didn't finish college?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.33,中文,,0,0,0,,史蒂夫·喬布斯也沒有啊\N{\r外文}Neither did Steve Jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我不討厭芬恩\N{\r外文}I do not hate Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我認為他是個很貼心的男孩\N{\r外文}I think he is a very sweet boy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.66,中文,,0,0,0,,很喜歡電子遊戲\N{\r外文}who loves video games
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.54,中文,,0,0,0,,而且聽說那啥很大\N{\r外文}and apparently has a large--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.20,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊 媽媽 你別說下去了\N{\r外文}Oh my God, Mom. You have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.95,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我不說了\N{\r外文}Okay, I'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:45.95,中文,,0,0,0,,現在不說了\N{\r外文}For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\r外文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.33,中文,,0,0,0,,不客氣\N{\r外文}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我也有消息要宣佈\N{\r外文}I have news too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.75,中文,,0,0,0,,復發了\N{\r外文}It's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.25,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.62,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r外文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.87,中文,,0,0,0,,好 那我們再它消滅掉不就行了\N{\r外文}Okay, so they'll just have to get rid of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.62,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\r外文}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我們再找別的醫生\N{\r外文}We'll find another doctor, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.00,中文,,0,0,0,,而且我看到文章說德國有一種療法\N{\r外文}And I read about these treatments they're doing in Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.87,中文,,0,0,0,,聽說非常有效\N{\r外文}that apparently are really effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我會放下工作 搬來和你一起住 亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}And I will stop working... -Alex. And move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我會一直照顧你 直到你好起來\N{\r外文}And I will take care of you until you get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:30.79,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\r外文}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:35.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不要去德國搞什麼神奇科技\N{\r外文}No magic treatments in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:40.08,中文,,0,0,0,,不要用什麼 比疾病本身難受十倍的療法\N{\r外文}No cure that's ten times worse than the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.62,中文,,0,0,0,,不會有什麼用的\N{\r外文}It's not going to make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.91,中文,,0,0,0,,這次不要這樣\N{\r外文}Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.37,中文,,0,0,0,,來抱抱我\N{\r外文}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我不在 你可怎麼辦啊\N{\r外文}What am I going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你不在 我可怎麼辦啊\N{\r外文}What am I going to do without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 親愛的\N{\r外文}Hey, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.87,中文,,0,0,0,,準備好露個面了嗎\N{\r外文}Ready to make an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你會沒事嗎\N{\r外文}Gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:17.12,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 山姆 很高興見到你 真的\N{\r外文}-Hi, Sam. It's good to see you. Really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你不覺得這很不真實嗎 什麼意思\N{\r外文}Don't you think it's surreal? How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:32.00,中文,,0,0,0,,所有人都跑來了這裏 可唯獨應該在這裏的人卻不在了\N{\r外文}All of these people here except the one person who's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:36.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直期待著她會從廚房走出來 叫我別再偷懶了\N{\r外文}I keep expecting her to walk out of the kitchen and tell me to stop slouching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我都不知道爸爸會過來\N{\r外文}I didn't know Dad was gonna be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.58,中文,,0,0,0,,他們結婚的20年中 大部分時間都很幸福\N{\r外文}They were married for 20 years, most of them, happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.70,中文,,0,0,0,,他當然會來了 隨便了\N{\r外文}-Of course he was gonna be there. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是很討厭他說得好像 離婚是他們雙方共同的決定\N{\r外文}I just hate when he talks as if the divorce was some kind of mutual decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,大哥 是你丟下了媽媽\N{\r外文}Like, bro, he left her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.25,中文,,0,0,0,,希望媽把分家產的事說清楚了\N{\r外文}I hope your mom was clear about dividing stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:00.20,中文,,0,0,0,,千萬別像尼爾森家那樣 他們已經不相往來了\N{\r外文}You don't wanna be like the Nelsons. They don't talk to each other anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:04.00,中文,,0,0,0,,對 只要把前廳塔馬約的畫給我 我就沒意見\N{\r外文}Agreed. As long as I get the Tamayo painting in the front hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:07.58,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽才剛走一個禮拜 你們卻滿嘴都是怎麼分東西\N{\r外文}God, Mom's barely been gone a week, and all you can talk about is her stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你這話說得輕鬆 你馬上就要繼承整個公司了\N{\r外文}That's easy for you to say. You're inheriting the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道 我才在那兒工作了一年\N{\r外文}You don't know that. I've barely worked a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:14.33,中文,,0,0,0,,不然你以為 凱瑟琳幹嘛要花這麼長時間訓練你\N{\r外文}Why do you think Catherine spent so much time training you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.08,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊 你把我說得跟個寵物似的\N{\r外文}God, you make me sound like a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.62,中文,,0,0,0,,住口 你們倆\N{\r外文}Stop it, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.37,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯在工作上的表現很棒\N{\r外文}Alex is doing great at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.79,中文,,0,0,0,,她對接下來的事 已經做好完全的準備了\N{\r外文}She's entirely ready for what's ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.41,中文,,0,0,0,,大家好 抱歉 我遲到了\N{\r外文}Hello, everyone. Apologies for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.41,中文,,0,0,0,,節哀順變\N{\r外文}I'd just like to say how truly sorry I am for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你是誰來著\N{\r外文}Uh, who are you exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我叫布拉德·阿克曼\N{\r外文}My name is Brad Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:54.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我幫助你們母親 完成了她遺囑的最終版本\N{\r外文}I worked with your mother on the final draft of her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.66,中文,,0,0,0,,老沙利文呢 沙利文先生在辦公室裏\N{\r外文}-Where's old man Sullivan? Mr. Sullivan is in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.75,中文,,0,0,0,,布拉德 對吧\N{\r外文}Um, it's Brad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.87,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你是這裏的合夥人嗎\N{\r外文}I'm sorry, but are you even a partner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我是副合夥人\N{\r外文}I'm an associate partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,或許應該要求看看他的法律學位證書\N{\r外文}Maybe we should ask to see his law degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你一定是亞歷克斯吧\N{\r外文}You must be Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.58,中文,,0,0,0,,讓我猜猜\N{\r外文}And let me guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.58,中文,,0,0,0,,朱利安 凱瑟琳 盧卡斯還有佐伊\N{\r外文}Julian, Catherine, Lucas, and Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.95,中文,,0,0,0,,恭喜你們喜得千金艾瑪\N{\r外文}Congratulations on the birth of your daughter, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\r外文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你們母親是一位了不起的女性\N{\r外文}Your mother was an amazing woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:27.75,中文,,0,0,0,,即便是生著病的時候 她依舊是那麼堅強 風趣\N{\r外文}Even when she was sick, she was so strong and funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.54,中文,,0,0,0,,可以這麼說\N{\r外文}and, I don't know if this makes any sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:34.58,中文,,0,0,0,,無論她說什麼做什麼 都有一種氣場\N{\r外文}present in everything that she said and did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:38.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我很榮幸 她選擇了讓我做她的遺產執行人\N{\r外文}I'm honored she chose me to be the executor of her estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:40.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我們開始吧\N{\r外文}Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.54,中文,,0,0,0,,"本人伊麗莎白·羅斯\N{\r外文}"I, Elizabeth Rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:46.08,中文,,0,0,0,,為美國公民 現居紐約布魯克林區\N{\r外文}a resident of Brooklyn, New York, and a citizen of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.25,中文,,0,0,0,,特此聲明 以下為我的最終遺囑"\N{\r外文}declare this to be my final will."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.79,中文,,0,0,0,,感覺好奇怪\N{\r外文}This is so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:54.50,中文,,0,0,0,,"我的洛布版柏拉圖全集留給朱利安\N{\r外文}"To Julian, I leave my Loeb edition of Plato's works."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:59.95,中文,,0,0,0,,提醒他一山還有一山高 不要自以為是\N{\r外文}"A gentle reminder that he may not always be the smartest person in the room."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:06.20,中文,,0,0,0,,塔馬約的畫能讓我們回想起家族傳統\N{\r外文}"The Tamayo painting, an evocative reminder of the heritage of our family,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:07.79,中文,,0,0,0,,留給佐伊\N{\r外文}I leave to Zoe."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,她可以跟盧卡斯分享 只要他永遠不離開她"\N{\r外文}"She can share it with Lucas, as long as he never leaves her."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:14.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我絕對不會的\N{\r外文}I would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.33,中文,,0,0,0,,接下來 是你們母親的房子\N{\r外文}Next is your mother's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:21.04,中文,,0,0,0,,"我希望房子本身與屋內的物品\N{\r外文}"It is my wish that neither the house nor its contents
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.50,中文,,0,0,0,,在接下來的12個月中 都不會被出售或出租\N{\r外文}be sold or leased for 12 months."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我的孩子們可以在此期間居住\N{\r外文}"My children may inhabit the home during this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.54,中文,,0,0,0,,但不得連續超過90天"\N{\r外文}but for no longer than 90 consecutive days."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.95,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 打擾一下\N{\r外文}Whoa, sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:32.04,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽有沒有說 為什麼想讓我們把房子留著\N{\r外文}Did our mother explain why she wanted us to keep the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望能永遠留著\N{\r外文}I wish we could keep it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.04,中文,,0,0,0,,這棟房子就是媽媽 也是我們的歷史\N{\r外文}The house is Mom. It's our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.54,中文,,0,0,0,,真貼心 亞歷克斯 你知道要繳多少稅嗎\N{\r外文}Yeah, that's sweet, Alex. Do you know what the taxes are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.04,中文,,0,0,0,,布拉德 你確定她知道費用多高嗎\N{\r外文}Brad, are you sure she understood how expensive this will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.16,中文,,0,0,0,,她專門安排了一筆款項 用以支付各項費用\N{\r外文}In fact, she made provisions to cover any costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.66,中文,,0,0,0,,接下來說一說"羅斯美妝"吧\N{\r外文}-Shall we move on to Rose Cosmetics?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:53.41,中文,,0,0,0,,"我孩子們所擁有的"羅斯美妝"股份 保持20%不變\N{\r外文}"My children's shares of Rose Cosmetics will stay at 20%."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:58.25,中文,,0,0,0,,剩餘的股份與首席執行官的職位 交給我的兒媳\N{\r外文}"The remaining shares and title of CEO will go to my daughter-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.95,中文,,0,0,0,,凱瑟琳·威廉姆斯·羅斯"\N{\r外文}Catherine Williams Rose."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 什麼\N{\r外文}Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:06.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你母親手上的"羅斯美妝"股份 將留給你的嫂子\N{\r外文}Your mother's remaining shares of Rose Cosmetics will go to your sister-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:07.87,中文,,0,0,0,,凱瑟琳\N{\r外文}Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:17.83,中文,,0,0,0,,她最後的指示是 凱瑟琳要任命一名新的營銷主管\N{\r外文}Her last directive is that Catherine appoint a new head of marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.95,中文,,0,0,0,,可我就是營銷主管啊\N{\r外文}ButI'mhead of marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.66,中文,,0,0,0,,今天之後就不是了\N{\r外文}Not after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:23.87,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我被開除了\N{\r外文}So I'm fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.58,中文,,0,0,0,,她從墳墓中把我開除了\N{\r外文}She's firing me from the grave? What...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,這不違法嗎\N{\r外文}Aren't there, like, laws or something against that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,"最後我心愛的女兒亞歷山德拉\N{\r外文}"Finally, my beloved daughter, Alexandra,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.08,中文,,0,0,0,,將在之後的指定日期領取遺產"\N{\r外文}is to collect her inheritance at a later date."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:44.50,中文,,0,0,0,,這裏有一個備註 我將私下向你解釋\N{\r外文}And there is an asterisk here which I'm meant to explain to you privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:45.45,中文,,0,0,0,,太離譜了\N{\r外文}This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你做遺囑業務多久了\N{\r外文}I mean, how long have you actually been doing wills and dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:52.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我這家事務所 已經做了三年的遺產規劃\N{\r外文}I've been doing estate planning at the firm for three years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:53.62,中文,,0,0,0,,三年 哇喔\N{\r外文}Three years. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.41,中文,,0,0,0,,相當於資深大佬了\N{\r外文}You're basically a regular Thurgood Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.66,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝您的誇獎 在下感激萬分\N{\r外文}That's nice, thank you. I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:01.41,中文,,0,0,0,,但還是別這樣跟我說話 好嗎 不然怎麼著 剝奪我的繼承權\N{\r外文}-Please don't talk to me like that. Or what? You'll take away my inheritance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你母親是一位非常有智慧的女性\N{\r外文}I'd like you to consider that your mother was a very intelligent woman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.87,中文,,0,0,0,,她最在乎的是怎麼做對你最好\N{\r外文}whose main concern is what's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.45,中文,,0,0,0,,解雇我是為我好 請你相信她\N{\r外文}-Right, as in firing me. Trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.91,中文,,0,0,0,,然後剝奪我的繼承權 她沒有剝奪你的繼承權\N{\r外文}-And disinheriting me. She did not disinherit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.79,中文,,0,0,0,,她是她唯一的女兒 卻什麼也沒拿到 連一件傢俱都沒有\N{\r外文}Her only daughter. And I get nothing. Not even a piece of furniture!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:20.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什麼 你以為我生氣是因為錢\N{\r外文}I know what you're thinking. You're thinking that this is about money
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.33,中文,,0,0,0,,還有珠寶什麼的 但事實是\N{\r外文}and jewelry and whatever. But the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:27.41,中文,,0,0,0,,昨天 我唯一想要的 就是她的床\N{\r外文}yesterday, the only thing that I wanted was her bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:31.08,中文,,0,0,0,,就這樣 我只想她那張搖搖晃晃的鐵床\N{\r外文}That's it. I just wanted her old rickety iron bed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.79,中文,,0,0,0,,這樣我就可以躺在上面 蜷縮起來\N{\r外文}so I could just lay in it and curl up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.66,中文,,0,0,0,,假裝她還跟我在一起\N{\r外文}and just pretend that she was still with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你和你母親的關係有多親密\N{\r外文}I know how close you and your mother were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.87,中文,,0,0,0,,她跟我說過很多次\N{\r外文}She told me many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.37,中文,,0,0,0,,她只是為你準備了一些別的東西\N{\r外文}She just had something else in mind for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:58.95,中文,,0,0,0,,這是什麼\N{\r外文}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.29,中文,,0,0,0,,（亞歷山德拉·羅斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:04.08,中文,,0,0,0,,她希望你在一個人的時候再打開\N{\r外文}She wanted you to open it when you were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你有視頻光碟播放機嗎\N{\r外文}Do you have a DVD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:10.45,中文,,0,0,0,,有 在櫃子裏 與錄音帶和手搖式黃油機放在一起\N{\r外文}Yeah. It's in the closet next to the VCR and the butter churn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我男朋友有一台Xbox遊戲機\N{\r外文}My boyfriend has an Xbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.45,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 那也行\N{\r外文}Yeah, that'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.62,中文,,0,0,0,,回家去 看看信封裏的東西\N{\r外文}Go home. See what's in the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.95,中文,,0,0,0,,希望你能明白媽媽的良苦用心\N{\r外文}Hopefully some of this will start to make some sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我的律師會和你保持聯繫\N{\r外文}My lawyer will be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我就是你的律師\N{\r外文}I... I am your lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:56.75,中文,,0,0,0,,芬恩\N{\r外文}Finn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.00,中文,,0,0,0,,有人嗎\N{\r外文}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:11.66,中文,,0,0,0,,（沙利文律所 亞歷山德拉·卡羅琳娜·羅斯收）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.66,中文,,0,0,0,,（致亞歷克斯 愛你的媽媽）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:35.79,中文,,0,0,0,,（生命清單）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.83,中文,,0,0,0,,（做一個好老師 幫助他人 紋身）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.16,中文,,0,0,0,,（在人群中狂舞 讀完《白鯨記》）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.29,中文,,0,0,0,,（找到真愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.79,中文,,0,0,0,,（致亞歷克斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:17:59.83,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 小豆子\N{\r外文}Hey, Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你一定氣炸了\N{\r外文}You must be so pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.79,中文,,0,0,0,,這不好笑 媽媽\N{\r外文}It's not funny, Mom, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:05.37,中文,,0,0,0,,這不好笑 我知道\N{\r外文}It's not funny, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:08.00,中文,,0,0,0,,聽我說原因 好嗎\N{\r外文}But I'm gonna explain, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:14.16,中文,,0,0,0,,上周 我正在安排我所謂的"後事"\N{\r外文}Last week, I was getting my so-called affairs in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:18.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天吶 人啊 總是會無緣無故留太多垃圾了\N{\r外文}Oh my God, the crap that we hold onto for no apparent reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:23.04,中文,,0,0,0,,那還是一次精彩的人生回顧啊 你知道嗎\N{\r外文}But it was actually this amazing life flashback. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,應該說是對你小時候的回顧\N{\r外文}I mean, it was actually ayouflashback.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.20,中文,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧我找到的這些東西\N{\r外文}I got to... Look at all this stuff I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:32.41,中文,,0,0,0,,看啊 這麼多你的手指畫 成績單\N{\r外文}Look, all your finger paintings, report cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:37.29,中文,,0,0,0,,而在這堆東西中 我找到了這張紙\N{\r外文}But in the middle of it all, I found this piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:40.41,中文,,0,0,0,,一張生命清單\N{\r外文}A life list.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你的生命清單\N{\r外文}Yourlife list.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這張清單\N{\r外文}I love this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:54.37,中文,,0,0,0,,這張清單反應了你是個怎樣的人\N{\r外文}This list is such a reflection of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我"曾"是個怎樣的人 我寫這個時才13歲\N{\r外文}Who I was. I was 13 when I wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我明白 你當然已經改變了\N{\r外文}And I know, obviously, you have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.62,中文,,0,0,0,,天吶 就好像她能聽到我說話一樣\N{\r外文}Oh my God, it's like she's listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.45,中文,,0,0,0,,這正是我擔憂的事\N{\r外文}And I think that's my concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:09.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你好像並沒有完成這些事項 並列出新的清單\N{\r外文}is that I don't know that you have replaced this with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你難道已經放棄了夢想和抱負\N{\r外文}I wonder, have you given up your dreams and your aspirations?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:17.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你的目標是什麼\N{\r外文}Your goals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.66,中文,,0,0,0,,別告訴我是"羅斯美妝"因為\N{\r外文}And don't tell me Rose Cosmetics, because
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我覺得因為我給了你這份舒適的工作\N{\r外文}I feel like I gave you this cozy job
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.50,中文,,0,0,0,,才讓你得以逃避真實的自己\N{\r外文}that allowed you to run away from who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:31.20,中文,,0,0,0,,非常感謝 好的 我們來看一下這張清單\N{\r外文}Thanks a lot. So okay, let's look at the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.66,中文,,0,0,0,,"幫助他人 作出貢獻"\N{\r外文}"Help people and make a difference."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.83,中文,,0,0,0,,"做一個好老師"\N{\r外文}"Be a great teacher."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.50,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 你天生就是個老師\N{\r外文}Alex, you are a born teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.58,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧"學會開車 紋一次身"你可以跳過 拜託 我的老天爺\N{\r外文}Okay, "learn to drive, get a tattoo."You can skip those, please, dear God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我唯一的要求\N{\r外文}My one request...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.87,中文,,0,0,0,,"找到真愛"\N{\r外文}"Find true love."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我怎麼覺得你連這個也放棄了\N{\r外文}Why do I have a horrible feeling you've given up on that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:55.66,中文,,0,0,0,,這話不公平\N{\r外文}That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能意識到自己有多麼優秀\N{\r外文}I want you to know how incredible you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能過上最好的生活\N{\r外文}I want you to live your best life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:05.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你必須從坑裏爬出來\N{\r外文}You have to get yourself out of this hole you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我沒在坑裏啊\N{\r外文}I'm not in a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:09.54,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 這沒得商量\N{\r外文}I'm sorry, that's not up for discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:13.24,中文,,0,0,0,,到時我不在了 沒辦法把你挖出來\N{\r外文}I'm not gonna be around to dig you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.87,中文,,0,0,0,,但我一定會留一把鏟子給你\N{\r外文}but I can sure as hell leave you a shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能完成這張清單 小豆子\N{\r外文}I want you to complete this list, Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.16,中文,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\r外文}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.91,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽 你不能撂下這些話 然後就\N{\r外文}Mom, you can't just say that and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:33.33,中文,,0,0,0,,好 你每完成一項清單事項\N{\r外文}Okay. Every time you check off something from the list,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.54,中文,,0,0,0,,布拉德就會給你一張視頻光碟\N{\r外文}Brad is going to give you one of these DVDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我馬上就要錄了\N{\r外文}which I am going to record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:44.29,中文,,0,0,0,,等整張清單都完成了之後 你將會得到這個信封\N{\r外文}And once the list is completely finished, you will get this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但時間不多了\N{\r外文}But the clock is ticking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:52.16,中文,,0,0,0,,清單必須在新年之前完成 否則就拿不到信封\N{\r外文}The list has to be finished by New Year's. Otherwise, no envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天 太離譜了\N{\r外文}Oh my God, I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是在開玩笑 小豆子\N{\r外文}I'm not screwing around, Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.12,中文,,0,0,0,,這是一件很嚴肅的事\N{\r外文}This is serious business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.50,中文,,0,0,0,,這是你的生命\N{\r外文}This is your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我愛你\N{\r外文}And I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我們下一張視頻光碟見\N{\r外文}See you on the next DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:22.87,中文,,0,0,0,,這也太瘋狂了\N{\r外文}This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:27.12,中文,,0,0,0,,"在人群中狂舞 和一名紐約尼克斯的球員單挑"\N{\r外文}"Go all out in a mosh pit.""Play one-on-one with a New York Knick."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.54,中文,,0,0,0,,"講單口相聲"跟我解釋一下這個\N{\r外文}"Do stand-up comedy."Walk me through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:34.62,中文,,0,0,0,,盧卡斯和我曾經發過誓 要去參加喜劇地窖的開放麥之夜\N{\r外文}Lucas and I once swore that we would do open mic night at the Comedy Cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.50,中文,,0,0,0,,當時寫的笑話我都還收著呢\N{\r外文}And... and I still have the jokes I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我必須要拜讀一下"跟爸爸和好"\N{\r外文}-I gonna need to read those. "Make peace with Dad."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:41.37,中文,,0,0,0,,"做一個好老師"這些你都能做到的\N{\r外文}"Be a great teacher."You can do these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你應該去做\N{\r外文}Mm-hmm. You should do these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.50,中文,,0,0,0,,為什麼 就為了能繼承一點錢\N{\r外文}Why? So I can inherit some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.50,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 不 這樣太噁心了\N{\r外文}-Yeah. No, it's just gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.58,中文,,0,0,0,,而且我已經發過誓 再也不會踏進教室半步\N{\r外文}Besides, I swore that I would never step foot into a classroom ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:54.50,中文,,0,0,0,,哎呀 管他呢 就去做個幾周代課老師唄\N{\r外文}Oh my God, who cares? Temp for a couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:58.33,中文,,0,0,0,,拉台舊電視機出來 放點《歷險小恐龍》不就搞定了\N{\r外文}Roll out one of those rickety TVs, pop onLand Before Time,and thenvoila.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:00.37,中文,,0,0,0,,或許能讓你再次喜歡上教書\N{\r外文}Or maybe you enjoy teaching again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:02.04,中文,,0,0,0,,不就是這麼個意思嗎\N{\r外文}Isn't that the idea here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.33,中文,,0,0,0,,反正不是我的意思\N{\r外文}Not my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 我跟你認識這麼久了\N{\r外文}Alex. I've known you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.25,中文,,0,0,0,,無論你是怎麼騙自己 你是永遠也不會喜歡經營那家公司的\N{\r外文}You'd never enjoy running that company, no matter what you tell yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,最愛你們這麼認真了\N{\r外文}Love when you guys get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.29,中文,,0,0,0,,"找到真愛"\N{\r外文}Hmm, "Find true love."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:15.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你愛芬恩 對吧\N{\r外文}You love Finn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.37,中文,,0,0,0,,他這麼貼心 這麼有趣\N{\r外文}He's so sweet, so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:19.70,中文,,0,0,0,,據說還有一個巨大的小雞雞\N{\r外文}Apparently has a ginormous willy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:23.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你倆在一起之後 都已經出了三款新蘋果手機了\N{\r外文}There's been three new iPhones since you've been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:26.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你應該知道 自己到底愛不愛他\N{\r外文}You should know by now if you love the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:30.20,中文,,0,0,0,,對 可同居本來就只是暫時的\N{\r外文}Yeah, but living together was just supposed to be like a temporary thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:34.54,中文,,0,0,0,,可後來媽媽病倒了 我就不自己找地方住了\N{\r外文}and then Mom got sick, and it just seemed, you know, easier not to find my own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:36.83,中文,,0,0,0,,可她就是這麼個意思\N{\r外文}Which is exactly what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:38.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你根本就沒有認真\N{\r外文}You're not dealing with shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:40.62,中文,,0,0,0,,比如不把清單的事告訴芬恩\N{\r外文}Like not telling Finn about the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.54,中文,,0,0,0,,還記得訂婚之前 盧卡斯和我分手那次嗎\N{\r外文}Do you remember when Lucas and I broke up before we got engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:48.70,中文,,0,0,0,,大家都記得安德森·庫珀 不是還做了一期特別節目嗎\N{\r外文}The whole world remembers. Didn't Anderson Cooper do a special?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:49.91,中文,,0,0,0,,真幽默\N{\r外文}Hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我去找你媽徵求意見 她把她的真愛測試告訴了我\N{\r外文}I asked your mom for advice, and she told me about her true love test.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:56.50,中文,,0,0,0,,還記得嗎\N{\r外文}Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:58.12,中文,,0,0,0,,有點印象\N{\r外文}Vaguely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:01.29,中文,,0,0,0,,是不是要問自己四個問題\N{\r外文}There's four questions you're supposed to ask yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,還是說那是逾越節\N{\r外文}Or is that Passover?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:05.33,中文,,0,0,0,,對 四個問題\N{\r外文}Yes, four questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:11.08,中文,,0,0,0,,第一 你能否把心中所想的一切都告訴他\N{\r外文}One, can you tell him everything in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:15.00,中文,,0,0,0,,第二 他善良嗎\N{\r外文}Two, is he kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:20.87,中文,,0,0,0,,第三 他會幫你成為最好的自己嗎\N{\r外文}Three, does he help you become the best version of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:22.66,中文,,0,0,0,,意思是\N{\r外文}Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:26.62,中文,,0,0,0,,芬恩能否幫助亞歷克斯全速飛行\N{\r外文}Alex in full flight with Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:33.00,中文,,0,0,0,,第四 你願意為他生孩子嗎\N{\r外文}Four, can you imagine him as the father of your children?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:39.16,中文,,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白要我問自己這些問題\N{\r外文}Elizabeth said to ask myself those questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.83,中文,,0,0,0,,如果盧卡斯通過了 說明我走對了路\N{\r外文}and if Lucas passed, I was on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:45.83,中文,,0,0,0,,這很瘋狂 我知道\N{\r外文}This is totally crazy. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:48.41,中文,,0,0,0,,但我相信你媽媽\N{\r外文}But I trust your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.62,0:23:52.37,中文,,0,0,0,,再說了 你還能有什麼損失呢\N{\r外文}Besides, what have you got to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:58.87,中文,,0,0,0,,芬恩善良嗎\N{\r外文}Is Finn kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:00.54,中文,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\r外文}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:04.54,中文,,0,0,0,,他會幫我成為最好的自己嗎\N{\r外文}Does he help me become the best version of myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:12.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我能否把心中所想的一切都告訴他\N{\r外文}Can I tell him everything in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.04,0:24:15.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我連自己都不告訴\N{\r外文}I can barely tell myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:21.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我願意為他生孩子嗎\N{\r外文}Can I imagine him being the father of our children?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.66,0:24:29.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你在搞什麼啊\N{\r外文}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.37,0:24:31.20,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 嘿 寶貝 嗨\N{\r外文}-Oh, hey, babe. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.29,0:24:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是在為我的遊戲做"嗨爆測試"\N{\r外文}I'm just, uh ...doing the stoner test of my game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.08,0:24:36.08,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼測試\N{\r外文}The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.58,0:24:37.75,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨爆測試\N{\r外文}The stoner test?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.83,0:24:40.70,中文,,0,0,0,,小青年喜歡抽嗨了之後玩遊戲\N{\r外文}Kids like to play video games stoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.79,0:24:43.83,中文,,0,0,0,,所以要做到嗨著玩時夠簡單\N{\r外文}so you have to make sure it's still easy enough while you're high,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:46.95,中文,,0,0,0,,不嗨時玩又極具挑戰性\N{\r外文}but still super challenging when you're not high.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.04,0:24:48.33,中文,,0,0,0,,懂我的意思不\N{\r外文}Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.62,0:24:51.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我有事要找你談\N{\r外文}I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.75,0:24:52.70,中文,,0,0,0,,非得現在嗎\N{\r外文}Like, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.83,0:24:54.79,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.00,0:25:01.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 用這個來激勵人 這算是天才之舉\N{\r外文}You know, as a life motivator, this is kind of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.12,0:25:03.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我覺得你應該去做 畢竟這是你的遺產\N{\r外文}I think you should totally go for it. I mean, it's your inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.95,0:25:04.95,中文,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 對\N{\r外文}-Really? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.04,0:25:08.16,中文,,0,0,0,,想想這能為你帶來多少自由 不 應該說為我倆\N{\r外文}Think about how much freedom it would give you. Both of us, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.25,0:25:10.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我終於可以完成 《美國殭屍》的設計工作\N{\r外文}I mean, I could finish designingAmerican Zombie,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.62,0:25:12.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以管理公司 不用教書了\N{\r外文}you'd run the company instead of teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.62,0:25:13.58,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼公司\N{\r外文}What company?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.66,0:25:15.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直在說的那個遊戲公司呀\N{\r外文}The gaming company I'm always talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.70,0:25:19.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以當品牌經理 我們就能每天24小時在一起了\N{\r外文}You'd be like the... the brander or whatever, and we'd hang 24-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.20,0:25:20.79,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 你是這麼看我的未來的\N{\r外文}Wait, is that how you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:23.87,中文,,0,0,0,,在你不存在的遊戲公司為你工作\N{\r外文}Working for you at your non-existent gaming company?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.95,0:25:25.95,中文,,0,0,0,,不 是我們的公司\N{\r外文}No, it's our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.04,0:25:28.50,中文,,0,0,0,,拜託 會很有趣的 再次一起工作\N{\r外文}Come on, it'd be fun working together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.58,0:25:32.08,中文,,0,0,0,,還記得在你開始糾結生死問題之前 我們有多開心嗎\N{\r外文}Remember when we used to have fun before your whole death fixation?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.16,0:25:33.54,中文,,0,0,0,,芬恩 我的母親剛剛過世\N{\r外文}Finn, my mother just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.62,0:25:38.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 但我覺得你該重新玩起來 因為玩是那麼的 那麼的\N{\r外文}I know, but I think you should try having fun again, because fun is so... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.54,0:25:39.79,中文,,0,0,0,,那麼的好玩 對\N{\r外文}-So fun? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.87,0:25:43.87,中文,,0,0,0,,玩很好玩 看到沒 拿這句話做公司的口號就很棒\N{\r外文}Fun's fun. That's actually... See, that's a great slogan for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.95,0:25:46.83,中文,,0,0,0,,而且 你口袋裏有了票子後 玩就更好玩了\N{\r外文}And fun's way more fun with some scratch in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.91,0:25:50.12,中文,,0,0,0,,要是將來我們有了孩子 怎麼養得起\N{\r外文}Like, say we want to have kids one day. How are we supposed to afford that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.20,0:25:52.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你現在又想生孩子了\N{\r外文}I'm sorry, now you want to have kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.45,0:25:54.41,中文,,0,0,0,,不太想 但我知道你會想的\N{\r外文}Not really, but I know you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.50,0:25:56.62,中文,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們還需要做什麼\N{\r外文}So what else do we have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:59.95,中文,,0,0,0,,在人群中狂舞 好棒\N{\r外文}Mosh pit? Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.04,0:26:01.62,中文,,0,0,0,,紋身\N{\r外文}Get tattoos?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.70,0:26:03.12,中文,,0,0,0,,要不紋個情侶的\N{\r外文}Why not matching?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.50,0:26:06.50,中文,,0,0,0,,找到真愛\N{\r外文}Find true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.83,0:26:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,寶貝 我現在就想去傢俱店裏 跟你做一場真正的愛\N{\r外文}Baby, I want to make true love to you right now on the Crate and Barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.62,0:26:14.50,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.50,0:26:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 拜託 你反應過頭了\N{\r外文}Alex, come on! You're totally overreacting!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:22.62,中文,,0,0,0,,上來 我們好好說\N{\r外文}Come up and let's talk about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.70,0:26:26.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你不用來遊戲公司工作 我是開玩笑的\N{\r外文}You don't have to work at the video game company. I was joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.75,0:26:27.91,中文,,0,0,0,,只是個玩笑\N{\r外文}It was a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.66,0:26:31.16,中文,,0,0,0,,只是為了好玩嘛\N{\r外文}It was a funny joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.50,0:26:45.83,中文,,0,0,0,,這下你開心了吧\N{\r外文}I hope you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.83,0:26:58.50,中文,,0,0,0,,（華爾街站）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.79,0:27:00.45,中文,,0,0,0,,不用 謝謝\N{\r外文}No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.29,0:27:05.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你母親一定會很開心的\N{\r外文}Your mother would be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.83,0:27:09.16,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 好吧 就像佐伊說的 我還能有什麼損失呢\N{\r外文}Yeah, well, like Zoe said, what have I got to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.25,0:27:13.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我現在單身 無業 而且我喜歡完成清單上的事項\N{\r外文}I'm single, unemployed, and I like crossing things off of lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:18.87,中文,,0,0,0,,而且只有這樣才能看到媽媽錄的光碟 對吧\N{\r外文}Plus, it's the only way that I get to see my mom's DVDs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.95,0:27:23.16,中文,,0,0,0,,對 每完成一項清單事項 就會給你一張視頻光碟\N{\r外文}Yes, there's another one waiting for you every time you do an item on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.25,0:27:25.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我能問你一件事嗎 問吧\N{\r外文}-Can I ask you something? Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.16,0:27:26.58,中文,,0,0,0,,視頻光碟 不是吧\N{\r外文}DVDs? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.66,0:27:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你母親希望能留給你 實實在在的 能夠保留下來的東西\N{\r外文}Your mother wanted you to have something tangible, you know, that you could keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.00,0:27:35.58,中文,,0,0,0,,那是你女朋友嗎\N{\r外文}Is that your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.66,0:27:37.62,中文,,0,0,0,,她叫妮娜 住在芝加哥\N{\r外文}Nina. She lives in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.70,0:27:38.70,中文,,0,0,0,,能看看嗎 可以\N{\r外文}-May I? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.33,0:27:42.16,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\r外文}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.25,0:27:46.25,中文,,0,0,0,,她真的很漂亮 你怎麼好像很意外似的\N{\r外文}-She's, like, really beautiful. You say that like it's a big surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.33,0:27:53.29,中文,,0,0,0,,她的顴骨真好看 身材近乎完美 而且\N{\r外文}Well, she has amazing cheekbones and what appears to be a perfect body. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.33,0:27:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你的領帶上沾著午餐吃的東西\N{\r外文}And you have lunch on your tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.75,0:27:57.58,中文,,0,0,0,,真幽默\N{\r外文}That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.66,0:28:00.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你要去講單口的時候 記得通知我\N{\r外文}You should let me know when you do the stand-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.41,0:28:01.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我這就把妮娜放回去\N{\r外文}I will put Nina back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.83,0:28:04.95,中文,,0,0,0,,以後我倆相處 你會一直是這麼個態度嗎\N{\r外文}Is this what it's going to be like with us the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.04,0:28:07.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是在按照你媽媽的要求做\N{\r外文}I'm just doing what your mom asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.95,0:28:08.79,中文,,0,0,0,,僅此而已\N{\r外文}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.75,0:28:10.62,中文,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\r外文}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.83,0:28:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,與此同時\N{\r外文}And in the meantime...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.83,0:28:17.75,中文,,0,0,0,,讀本書能有多難啊\N{\r外文}How hard can it be to read a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.83,0:28:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,糟糕\N{\r外文}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.95,0:28:53.12,中文,,0,0,0,,（學會彈《月光》 這樣媽媽才能不嘮叨）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:10.62,中文,,0,0,0,,（做一個好老師）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.70,0:29:13.87,中文,,0,0,0,,（紐約市公立學校 目前沒有職位空缺）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:20.33,中文,,0,0,0,,（紋身）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.58,0:29:47.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直不停地在失去朋友\N{\r外文}I keep losing friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.29,0:29:50.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我就像是友誼界的近藤麻理惠\N{\r外文}-I'm like the Marie Kondo of friendships...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.41,0:29:52.70,中文,,0,0,0,,如果近藤麻理惠 是被丟出去的那個的話\N{\r外文}...if Marie Kondo was the one getting thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.79,0:29:53.75,中文,,0,0,0,,第一次\N{\r外文}First time?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:55.83,中文,,0,0,0,,有一天我遇到了一個朋友 然後\N{\r外文}I ran into a friend the other day, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.91,0:29:56.83,中文,,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\r外文}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.91,0:29:58.66,中文,,0,0,0,,她氣色很好 挺了個小肚子\N{\r外文}She looked great. She had a baby bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.75,0:30:01.00,中文,,0,0,0,,就算冷場也沒事 至少你很美\N{\r外文}Even if you bomb, you look amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.08,0:30:04.37,中文,,0,0,0,,"我都不知道你懷孕了"就像你的T恤 很火辣\N{\r外文}"Didn't know you were expecting."Like your T-shirt. It's really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.45,0:30:06.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我絕對願意跟你的T恤上床\N{\r外文}I'd totally bang your T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.87,0:30:07.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟他上過床\N{\r外文}I slept with him.
