Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.66,0:32:11.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎麼來了 是你邀請我的\N{\r外文}-What are you doing here? Uh, you invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.75,0:32:14.04,中文,,0,0,0,,是嗎 希望你喜歡看車禍現場\N{\r外文}Did I? I hope you enjoyed the train wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.12,0:32:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不能算是車禍現場 最後大家被你逗笑了\N{\r外文}That wasn't a train wreck. You got that... that laugh. At the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.41,0:32:21.29,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你會得到一張光碟\N{\r外文}And you get one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.41,0:32:24.16,中文,,0,0,0,,完成一張 還剩11張\N{\r外文}One down, 11 to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.75,0:32:28.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我就知道 我不小心邀請你來是有原因的\N{\r外文}I knew I accidentally invited you for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.83,0:32:32.12,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 小豆子\N{\r外文}Hi, Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.20,0:32:35.29,中文,,0,0,0,,要是能看到你站在那舞台上 我真是做什麼都願意啊\N{\r外文}I would've given anything to have seen you on that stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.37,0:32:37.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你一定嚇死了吧\N{\r外文}Scared shitless, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.62,0:32:39.45,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.54,0:32:41.00,中文,,0,0,0,,但又充滿活力 對吧\N{\r外文}But alive, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.75,0:32:45.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你以前是個無所畏懼的孩子\N{\r外文}You were such a... a fearless kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.50,0:32:47.41,中文,,0,0,0,,後來怎麼變了呢\N{\r外文}What do you think happened to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.50,0:32:48.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\r外文}I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.41,0:32:50.54,中文,,0,0,0,,因為生活吧\N{\r外文}Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.62,0:32:53.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我想你是經歷了一些不小的挫折\N{\r外文}I think you suffered some real setbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.95,0:32:55.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我能理解\N{\r外文}And I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.87,0:33:02.37,中文,,0,0,0,,但我看著你逐漸開始安於 那些安全又不那麼痛苦的事\N{\r外文}But I watched you gradually start to settle for what was safe and less painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.45,0:33:07.62,中文,,0,0,0,,可是啊 親愛的 妥協無法讓恐懼和痛苦消失\N{\r外文}But, honey, settling is never gonna make the fear and the pain go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.70,0:33:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,這是我的經驗之談\N{\r外文}And I can tell you that from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.29,0:33:12.50,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我希望你嘗試這樣去做\N{\r外文}So I want you to try something for me.
