Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:30.50,中文,,0,0,0,,可怕極了\N{\r外文}Terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.25,0:33:32.50,中文,,0,0,0,,但也能改變人生\N{\r外文}But life-changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.70,0:33:35.45,中文,,0,0,0,,明白嗎 明白了\N{\r外文}-Got it? Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.16,0:33:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我們下一張視頻光碟再見\N{\r外文}I will see you on the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.20,0:33:40.20,中文,,0,0,0,,通話結束\N{\r外文}Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.75,0:33:49.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道我是否能受得了 每天都要做一件可怕的事\N{\r外文}You know what, I don't know if I can handle doing something scary every day
