Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.91,0:33:55.58,中文,,0,0,0,,如果能從助理那兒弄到點抗焦慮藥 或許我能一周做兩件吧\N{\r外文}I could maybe do it twice a week if I got some Xanax from my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.12,0:33:57.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你會先做什麼\N{\r外文}What would you do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.37,0:34:00.66,中文,,0,0,0,,很簡單 我會直接走進老沙利文的辦公室\N{\r外文}That's easy. I would go straight into old man Sullivan's office
