Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.91,0:36:54.04,中文,,0,0,0,,不要落下核心科目的進度\N{\r外文}and up to speed on core subjects while they're living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.12,0:36:56.29,中文,,0,0,0,,他們有時住幾周 有時甚至幾個月 嗯\N{\r外文}-Which could be weeks, sometimes months. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.37,0:36:58.75,中文,,0,0,0,,這裏面是 每一個孩子的課程安排和檔案\N{\r外文}Lesson plans and files for each child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.83,0:37:02.45,中文,,0,0,0,,稍後會介紹你認識 心理治療師泰勒醫生\N{\r外文}Later you'll meet with Dr. Taylor, one of our consulting therapists.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.54,0:37:04.45,中文,,0,0,0,,有什麼需要 儘管提出來\N{\r外文}Anything else you need, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.54,0:37:07.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不過我的回答大概是沒辦法解決\N{\r外文}Then I'll tell you why you probably can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.08,0:37:09.08,中文,,0,0,0,,祝你好運\N{\r外文}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.70,0:37:17.54,中文,,0,0,0,,（之後的安排 關於二級節奏的論文）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.16,0:37:40.37,中文,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\r外文}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.45,0:37:42.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我是羅斯老師\N{\r外文}I'm Miss Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.41,0:37:47.08,中文,,0,0,0,,各位 能安靜點嗎 我們要開始上課了\N{\r外文}Hey, guys, can we just please quiet down so we can get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.16,0:37:48.33,中文,,0,0,0,,亞倫\N{\r外文}Whoa! Aaron!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.91,0:37:51.12,中文,,0,0,0,,亞倫 別這樣 把毛衣還我\N{\r外文}Aaron, come on. Give me my sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.20,0:37:53.91,中文,,0,0,0,,請你把毛衣還給她 這一點也不好笑\N{\r外文}-Can you please give her the sweater? It's not even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.00,0:37:56.20,中文,,0,0,0,,亞倫 別這樣 粉色又不適合你\N{\r外文}Aaron, come on, man. Pink's not even your color.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.50,0:38:02.00,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝 女王陛下 謝謝\N{\r外文}-Thank you, Your Majesty. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.08,0:38:05.58,中文,,0,0,0,,有些人認為《哈姆雷特》是一部關於猶豫不決的戲劇\N{\r外文}Some people think Hamletis a play about indecision.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.66,0:38:10.16,中文,,0,0,0,,就是你無法在愛德華和雅各布之間 做出選擇的那種感覺\N{\r外文}You know, the feeling when you can't decide between Edward and Jacob,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.25,0:38:12.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道今天流行的帥吸血鬼叫啥\N{\r外文}or whoever the hot vampires are these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.00,0:38:15.83,中文,,0,0,0,,羅斯老師 你的例子得與時俱進啊\N{\r外文}Miss Rose, you gotta update your references.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.95,0:38:20.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望每個人都寫一篇作文\N{\r外文}So I want everyone to write about a time
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.41,0:38:23.33,中文,,0,0,0,,講述曾幾何時 自己有一件非常重要的事要做\N{\r外文}when they had something really important to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.41,0:38:25.25,中文,,0,0,0,,但就像哈姆雷特一樣\N{\r外文}But like Hamlet,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.33,0:38:27.50,中文,,0,0,0,,當時的你沒辦法採取行動\N{\r外文}you couldn't quite find a way to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.58,0:38:28.83,中文,,0,0,0,,給你們30分鐘時間\N{\r外文}You have 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.29,0:38:44.16,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 畫得真美\N{\r外文}Wow, that's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.25,0:38:45.25,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\r外文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.62,0:38:49.70,中文,,0,0,0,,但這不是我們要做的作業 對嗎 以斯拉\N{\r外文}But it's not the assignment we're doing, is it, Ezra?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.70,0:38:51.70,中文,,0,0,0,,隨便吧\N{\r外文}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.16,0:38:55.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 這個詞用在《哈姆雷特》上挺合適的\N{\r外文}You know, that's not a bad word for thinking aboutHamlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.54,0:38:59.41,中文,,0,0,0,,何不從這個詞開始寫呢 或許因為我根本不在乎\N{\r外文}-Why not use it as a starting point? Maybe 'cause I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.29,0:39:02.91,中文,,0,0,0,,或許因為"生存還是毀滅"是個愚蠢的問題\N{\r外文}Maybe because "to be or not to be"is a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.00,0:39:04.66,中文,,0,0,0,,或許吧\N{\r外文}Hmm. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.37,0:39:08.29,中文,,0,0,0,,又或許這是最重要的問題\N{\r外文}Or maybe it's the most important question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.75,0:39:13.25,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 如果你不同意我的話 或許你可以把反駁寫下來\N{\r外文}And hey, if you don't agree with me, then maybe you can write about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.16,0:39:17.33,中文,,0,0,0,,在此期間 讓我進一步沉浸在你美麗的畫作中吧\N{\r外文}In the meantime, I will take a deeper dive into your beautiful art.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.41,0:39:18.58,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 還給我\N{\r外文}Hey, give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.66,0:39:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,沒問題 等你寫完就還\N{\r外文}Absolutely, the second you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.37,0:39:22.75,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\r外文}Ah! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.95,0:39:26.75,中文,,0,0,0,,以斯拉 你幹什麼 採取行動\N{\r外文}-Ezra, what do you think you're doing? Taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.16,0:39:30.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\r外文}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.62,0:39:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,他不肯做作業 還對我豎中指\N{\r外文}He wouldn't do the assignment, and then he gave me the finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.12,0:39:35.04,中文,,0,0,0,,因為你拿走了他最珍貴的東西\N{\r外文}Only after you took away his prized possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.12,0:39:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,可我又不知道 在我叫你讀的檔案裏寫著\N{\r外文}-Right, but I didn't know that. It was in the folder I asked you to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.20,0:39:39.66,中文,,0,0,0,,上課前十分鐘才給的\N{\r外文}Ten minutes before class.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.75,0:39:42.87,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 這些孩子的心理非常脆弱\N{\r外文}Alex, these children are in a very vulnerable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.95,0:39:46.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你首先必須明白這一點 才能在這裏教書\N{\r外文}Before anything else, you have to understand that if this is gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.29,0:39:49.83,中文,,0,0,0,,霍華德老師 我能教這些孩子 我想教 請不要開除我\N{\r外文}Ms. Howard, I can teach these kids. I want to teach them. Please don't fire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.91,0:39:50.91,中文,,0,0,0,,誰要被開除啊\N{\r外文}Who's getting fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.00,0:39:52.75,中文,,0,0,0,,沒人 暫時\N{\r外文}Nobody. Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.83,0:39:55.95,中文,,0,0,0,,這位是亞歷克斯·羅斯 布拉德·阿克曼推薦的老師\N{\r外文}This is Alex Rose, the teacher recommended by Brad Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.04,0:39:58.79,中文,,0,0,0,,今天是她的第一天 不是特別的順利\N{\r外文}And it's her first day, and it's not going particularly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.87,0:40:02.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我記得你在這兒的第一天 不對 第一個星期我都記得\N{\r外文}Well, I remember your first day, Carol. Actually, I remember the whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.08,0:40:02.91,中文,,0,0,0,,很幽默\N{\r外文}Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.00,0:40:05.54,中文,,0,0,0,,要不你幫亞歷克斯 熟悉一下這邊的情況\N{\r外文}Maybe you can help Alex get the hang of how things work?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.62,0:40:07.25,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 我很樂意\N{\r外文}Yeah, I'd be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.33,0:40:08.58,中文,,0,0,0,,《白鯨記》女\N{\r外文}Girl withMoby Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.33,0:40:12.83,中文,,0,0,0,,這樣說好像有點問題\N{\r外文}That did not come out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.87,0:40:16.58,中文,,0,0,0,,以斯拉媽媽去年去世了 然後他和他姑姑搬了進來\N{\r外文}Ezra's mom died last year, and he and his aunt are here
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.66,0:40:19.75,中文,,0,0,0,,因為她有複雜的家庭情況要處理\N{\r外文}while she sorts out a complicated family situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.83,0:40:21.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我母親最近去世了\N{\r外文}My mother died recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.50,0:40:22.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我很遺憾\N{\r外文}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.95,0:40:24.91,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝 但我在想\N{\r外文}Thank you. Uh, but I'm thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.00,0:40:27.29,中文,,0,0,0,,或許我可以跟他聊聊這個共同點\N{\r外文}maybe it's something I could connect with him about.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.37,0:40:29.45,中文,,0,0,0,,對 這主意不錯\N{\r外文}Yeah, it's not a bad idea. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.54,0:40:32.62,中文,,0,0,0,,但最好先等一下\N{\r外文}I'd just wait a little bit before trying it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.37,0:40:35.41,中文,,0,0,0,,可我 像以斯拉這樣的孩子有點像貓\N{\r外文}-But I- Kids like Ezra are a bit like cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.00,0:40:38.70,中文,,0,0,0,,像貓 你必須等他們主動來找你\N{\r外文}-Like cats? You have to wait for them to come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.79,0:40:40.66,中文,,0,0,0,,即便你身體內的每個細胞\N{\r外文}Even when everything in your body
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.75,0:40:43.83,中文,,0,0,0,,都迫切想讓你去撓他們的耳朵\N{\r外文}is screaming out to scratch them behind their ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.91,0:40:45.70,中文,,0,0,0,,耐心 是美德\N{\r外文}-Patience- ...is a virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.79,0:40:48.87,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我還在慢慢熟悉這個概念\N{\r外文}-Right. Yeah, the one that I'm still getting acquainted with.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.79,0:40:52.70,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 泰勒醫生\N{\r外文}Thank you, Dr. Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.79,0:40:54.25,中文,,0,0,0,,不客氣 羅斯老師\N{\r外文}Anytime, Miss Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.33,0:40:55.45,中文,,0,0,0,,叫我亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.54,0:40:56.54,中文,,0,0,0,,叫我加勒特\N{\r外文}Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.25,0:40:59.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我們把剩下的檔案過一下吧\N{\r外文}Should we do the rest of these files?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.04,0:41:00.87,中文,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\r外文}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.95,0:41:03.62,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 哎呀 不行\N{\r外文}Yeah. Oh shit, I mean, I-I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.70,0:41:08.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我以為六點就能結束 所以約了人晚餐\N{\r外文}I... I thought we'd be done at six, and I have a dinner date to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.16,0:41:10.87,中文,,0,0,0,,約了我爸吃晚餐\N{\r外文}With my dad. I have dinner with... with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.95,0:41:13.33,中文,,0,0,0,,要不我們下一次\N{\r外文}But can we maybe try again?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.41,0:41:16.00,中文,,0,0,0,,可以 我每週一和週四都會在\N{\r外文}Yeah, I'm here Mondays and Thursdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.58,0:41:19.33,中文,,0,0,0,,或者你可以隨時打給我\N{\r外文}Or you can call me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.37,0:41:22.37,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 爸爸\N{\r外文}Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.58,0:41:24.79,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r外文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.87,0:41:27.00,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 地鐵上出了點問題\N{\r外文}Sorry, there was a problem on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.08,0:41:30.04,中文,,0,0,0,,每次都提早一點 這樣就不會\N{\r外文}Well, always leave a little extra time, then there won't be--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.12,0:41:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,就不會有問題了 我知道\N{\r外文}...be any problems, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.20,0:41:34.83,中文,,0,0,0,,可是沒了問題的人生 會有點無聊 不是嗎\N{\r外文}But a life without problems would be kind of boring, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.91,0:41:37.79,中文,,0,0,0,,是 我會好好思考\N{\r外文}Yeah. I'll take that under consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.87,0:41:39.83,中文,,0,0,0,,來吧 你還好嗎\N{\r外文}Come on. How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.37,0:41:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,挺好的\N{\r外文}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.33,0:41:44.83,中文,,0,0,0,,女性庇護所 很特別啊\N{\r外文}A women's shelter. That's... different.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.91,0:41:48.00,中文,,0,0,0,,但挺好的 我很高興你又開始教書了\N{\r外文}But good. Good. I'm happy you're teaching again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.08,0:41:50.62,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝 前提是我不被開除\N{\r外文}Thanks. Now if I could just manage not getting fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.70,0:41:53.08,中文,,0,0,0,,別這樣 亞歷克斯 拜託 我怎麼了\N{\r外文}-Well, don't do that, Alex. Come on. What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.16,0:41:56.41,中文,,0,0,0,,不要自我貶低 你是成年人了 這樣不幽默也不討喜\N{\r外文}That self-deprecating. It's not funny or charming. You're an adult now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.50,0:41:57.83,中文,,0,0,0,,以前你就覺得幽默了\N{\r外文}Did you ever think it was funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.91,0:41:59.25,中文,,0,0,0,,不 並不覺得 對嘛\N{\r外文}-Not really. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.33,0:42:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,但正如你媽以前常說的 我的幽默感有點\N{\r外文}But as your mother used to say, my sense of humor's a little... Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.08,0:42:07.50,中文,,0,0,0,,她真的很希望 我們能相處得更融洽一點\N{\r外文}You know, she really wanted us to get along better.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.16,0:42:09.91,中文,,0,0,0,,不要互相生氣\N{\r外文}Not be so angry with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.00,0:42:12.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我完全贊成 而且我沒有生你的氣\N{\r外文}I'm all for it. And... and I'm not angry with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.70,0:42:15.25,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 有時候我只是有些沮喪\N{\r外文}Okay, sometimes a little frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.33,0:42:17.95,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸我真的在很努力 為自己開闢出一條新的道路\N{\r外文}Thing is, Dad, I'm really trying to make this new path for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.04,0:42:22.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你能夠 支持我一下\N{\r外文}and I'd just like to feel that you could, you know, support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.45,0:42:26.29,中文,,0,0,0,,盧卡斯把遺囑的事告訴我了 當然了 你有需要儘管開口\N{\r外文}Lucas told me about the will. And of course, anything that you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.37,0:42:28.45,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不是錢\N{\r外文}No, not money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.54,0:42:31.45,中文,,0,0,0,,是情感上的支持 爸爸 天啊\N{\r外文}Emotional support, Dad. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.70,0:42:35.75,中文,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\r外文}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.70,0:42:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,看來愛生氣的人是你 不是我 我沒生氣\N{\r外文}-It seems you're the angry one, not me. I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.12,0:42:41.62,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 可能是有點\N{\r外文}Okay, fine, maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.70,0:42:43.04,中文,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢\N{\r外文}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.58,0:42:48.37,中文,,0,0,0,,在內心深處 我總覺得我達不到你的期望\N{\r外文}At some basic level, I always feel like I'm letting you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.58,0:42:52.87,中文,,0,0,0,,還記得我當時跟你說 我不想再當老師了嗎\N{\r外文}Do you remember when I told you I was gonna quit teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.95,0:42:53.79,中文,,0,0,0,,記得\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.87,0:42:56.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟我說的原話是 你一點也不驚訝\N{\r外文}You literally told me that you weren't surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.66,0:42:57.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不是 就是\N{\r外文}-No. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.58,0:42:59.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我說我很失望\N{\r外文}No, I said I was disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.58,0:43:01.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你遇到了一些波折\N{\r外文}Look, you had a few bumps along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.20,0:43:03.95,中文,,0,0,0,,結果就放棄了自己熱愛的事業\N{\r外文}and you gave up on a career that you cared deeply about.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.54,0:43:06.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼做 騙騙你 抱一抱你\N{\r外文}Like, what was I to do, lie and give you a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.50,0:43:10.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我無意冒犯 但這種事你媽交給你媽就行\N{\r外文}Come on, no disrespect, but your mother had that covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.12,0:43:12.83,中文,,0,0,0,,對 因為有哪個腦子正常的人 會在孩子被不公正地解雇後\N{\r外文}Right, 'cause who in their right mind would hug their kid
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.91,0:43:15.29,中文,,0,0,0,,擁抱一下自家孩子啊\N{\r外文}after they've just been unfairly fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.37,0:43:17.16,中文,,0,0,0,,而且 媽媽從來沒騙過我\N{\r外文}Also, Mom never lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.25,0:43:18.41,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 別開玩笑了\N{\r外文}Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.50,0:43:20.87,中文,,0,0,0,,隨便了 跟你和好是她的主意\N{\r外文}Whatever, this was her idea of working things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.95,0:43:23.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你以為你媽有多完美 她是挺棒的\N{\r外文}-You think your mom was so damn perfect. She was pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.54,0:43:25.29,中文,,0,0,0,,千萬別有人說她壞話\N{\r外文}Yeah, God forbid anyone should say a word
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.37,0:43:28.33,中文,,0,0,0,,把她從神壇上拉下來 但我向你保證\N{\r外文}that would knock her off her majestic pedestal, but I promise you, Alex,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.41,0:43:30.79,中文,,0,0,0,,她並不完美 她不是一個聖人\N{\r外文}she was not perfect, and she was not a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.87,0:43:34.04,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 真的嗎 她做了什麼糟糕的事\N{\r外文}Oh really? What? What did she do that was so terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.12,0:43:36.37,中文,,0,0,0,,她讓狗吃了你的艾迪鮑爾拖鞋\N{\r外文}What, she let the dog eat your Eddie Bauer slippers?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.45,0:43:38.75,中文,,0,0,0,,這一點也不好笑 沒交圖書館的罰款\N{\r外文}-That's not funny. Didn't pay her library fines?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.83,0:43:42.16,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 她逃稅了 不對 她出軌了\N{\r外文}Oh, she cheated on her taxes. No, wait, cheated on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.20,0:43:47.58,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\r外文}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.66,0:43:50.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 麻煩買單\N{\r外文}Excuse me, can I get the check, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.62,0:43:51.45,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\r外文}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.33,0:43:57.87,中文,,0,0,0,,是她出軌 你一直是這麼說的 對吧\N{\r外文}She cheated on you, that's what you're saying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.37,0:44:01.33,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你不能這樣扔個炸彈就走啊\N{\r外文}Dad, you can't just drop a bomb like that and walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.91,0:44:04.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你們離婚的時候我才15歲 就是那時候發生的嗎\N{\r外文}I was 15 when you got divorced, is that when it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.54,0:44:06.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要逃避我 停下來\N{\r外文}Why are you running away from me? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.08,0:44:10.08,中文,,0,0,0,,婚姻中難免會發生一些事 亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Things happen in a marriage, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.79,0:44:14.70,中文,,0,0,0,,但我們挺過來了 一起幸福地生活了很多年\N{\r外文}But we got through it, and we managed to have some pretty good years together,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.79,0:44:16.79,中文,,0,0,0,,其他的就別說了 好嗎\N{\r外文}so can we please just leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.87,0:44:17.83,中文,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\r外文}No, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.41,0:44:21.75,中文,,0,0,0,,求你了 我需要知道\N{\r外文}Please, I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.29,0:44:26.79,中文,,0,0,0,,事情發生在你出生以前\N{\r外文}It was before you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.62,0:44:31.00,中文,,0,0,0,,並不是出軌那麼簡單 而是\N{\r外文}It wasn't just a fling. Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.54,0:44:38.08,中文,,0,0,0,,發生了別的事\N{\r外文}Something else happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.75,0:44:40.66,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\r外文}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.29,0:44:44.50,中文,,0,0,0,,要不我們一起散散步吧 親愛的\N{\r外文}Why don't we go for a walk, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.00,0:45:05.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟我開玩笑嗎\N{\r外文}Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.87,0:45:09.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我沒聽錯吧\N{\r外文}Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.58,0:45:11.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你是說爸爸\N{\r外文}You're saying that Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.41,0:45:12.83,中文,,0,0,0,,不是我的親生父親\N{\r外文}...is not actually my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.70,0:45:19.87,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽與一個音樂人有過婚外情 他叫約翰尼·阿爾瓦雷斯\N{\r外文}Mom had an affair with a musician named Johnny Alvarez.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.70,0:45:23.62,中文,,0,0,0,,據說他以前在 格林威治村的一家俱樂部裏演出\N{\r外文}Apparently he played at a club they'd go to in the Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.45,0:45:26.41,中文,,0,0,0,,這真是\N{\r外文}Um, that's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.00,0:45:28.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我都不知道該說什麼了\N{\r外文}I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.95,0:45:31.33,中文,,0,0,0,,約翰尼·阿爾瓦雷斯\N{\r外文}Johnny Alvarez?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.37,0:45:33.62,中文,,0,0,0,,看來媽媽喜歡這種類型\N{\r外文}Sounds like Mom had a type.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.70,0:45:34.62,中文,,0,0,0,,盧卡斯\N{\r外文}Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.70,0:45:37.20,中文,,0,0,0,,她懷孕之後 就結束了這段關係\N{\r外文}She ended the relationship when she got pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.29,0:45:43.58,中文,,0,0,0,,她跟爸爸說好 不把這事告訴我 不告訴我們任何人\N{\r外文}and she and Dad made this agreement not to tell me. Or any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.66,0:45:46.29,中文,,0,0,0,,這就是他們拯救婚姻的辦法\N{\r外文}Like that was the way that they could save their marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.83,0:45:50.54,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 你現在的心情一定很複雜\N{\r外文}Alex, I can't imagine how difficult it must be to make sense of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.62,0:45:53.62,中文,,0,0,0,,介於麻木與出離憤怒之間吧\N{\r外文}I'm somewhere between numb and completely furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.00,0:45:56.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我到底是誰啊\N{\r外文}Like, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.33,0:46:00.87,中文,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有人告訴我 媽媽為什麼不告訴我\N{\r外文}And why didn't anyone, namely Mom, bother to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.16,0:46:04.00,中文,,0,0,0,,難怪我和爸爸的關係會是這樣\N{\r外文}It definitely explains a lot about me and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.08,0:46:06.08,中文,,0,0,0,,難怪他不像愛你們那樣愛我\N{\r外文}Why he never could love me the same as you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.16,0:46:09.33,中文,,0,0,0,,不是的 不是這樣的 好嗎\N{\r外文}-No. Hey, that is not true, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.41,0:46:11.79,中文,,0,0,0,,他依舊是你爸爸 是他把你養大\N{\r外文}And he's still your father. He's the man who raised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.91,0:46:13.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼辦\N{\r外文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.83,0:46:17.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我想我得找到他\N{\r外文}I think I need to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.25,0:46:19.00,中文,,0,0,0,,這樣恐怕不太好\N{\r外文}I'm not sure that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.08,0:46:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,朱利安 你怎麼能這麼說\N{\r外文}Julian, how can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.79,0:46:22.91,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯應該知道她的親生父親是誰\N{\r外文}Alex should know who her biological father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.00,0:46:25.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我明白 但我們公司是值得信賴的家族品牌\N{\r外文}I know, but the company is a trusted family brand...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.04,0:46:27.58,中文,,0,0,0,,目前正 怎麼\N{\r外文}...going through... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.66,0:46:31.04,中文,,0,0,0,,公司正處於重大變動之中 現在如果這個故事傳出去\N{\r外文}It's going through a big transition right now, and if the story gets out--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.12,0:46:32.62,中文,,0,0,0,,故事 你在開玩笑嗎\N{\r外文}The story? Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.70,0:46:38.45,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 我們都會盡最大的能力 幫你解決這個問題\N{\r外文}Alex, we are all going to do whatever we have to do to help you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.54,0:46:40.00,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我不是那個意思\N{\r外文}Okay, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.08,0:46:43.45,中文,,0,0,0,,天吶 為什麼每次總是我做壞人啊 因為你太他媽擅長了\N{\r外文}-Jesus, why am I always the bad guy? Because you're so fucking good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.33,0:46:55.29,中文,,0,0,0,,朱利安不是那個意思\N{\r外文}Julian didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.20,0:46:58.50,中文,,0,0,0,,他只是最近過得很辛苦\N{\r外文}He's just been having a really hard time lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.58,0:46:59.45,中文,,0,0,0,,辛苦什麼\N{\r外文}With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.54,0:47:01.29,中文,,0,0,0,,養育兩個優秀的孩子\N{\r外文}Raising two wonderful children?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.12,0:47:03.66,中文,,0,0,0,,有一個完美的妻子\N{\r外文}Being married to the perfect woman
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.75,0:47:07.12,中文,,0,0,0,,搶走了我並不勝任的好工作\N{\r外文}who took the perfect job that I was apparently unfit to handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.20,0:47:09.41,中文,,0,0,0,,他過得辛苦 是因為他母親去世了\N{\r外文}A hard time that his mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.83,0:47:13.95,中文,,0,0,0,,想念她的人不只你一個\N{\r外文}You're not the only one missing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.29,0:47:37.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我找布拉德·阿克曼\N{\r外文}I'm here to see Brad Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.95,0:47:39.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我是亞歷克斯·羅斯 有預約嗎\N{\r外文}I'm Alex Rose. Is he expecting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.45,0:47:42.04,中文,,0,0,0,,沒 但我敢肯定如果你 亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}-No, but I'm sure if you- Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.12,0:47:44.00,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 我們預約了嗎\N{\r外文}-Hey! Did we have an appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.08,0:47:45.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我正打算去買東西\N{\r外文}I-I was just about to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.04,0:47:50.83,中文,,0,0,0,,妮娜下周要過來 我覺得正是時候換條新領帶了\N{\r外文}Nina's coming into town next week, and I thought it was time for a new tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.91,0:47:52.87,中文,,0,0,0,,因為我說的話嗎 對\N{\r外文}-Because of what I said? Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.95,0:47:57.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直都希望 自己哪怕能改變一個人的人生也好\N{\r外文}You know, I always hoped, if only I could change just one person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.50,0:47:59.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你來有什麼事嗎\N{\r外文}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.12,0:48:00.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我讀完了《白鯨記》\N{\r外文}Uh, I finishedMoby Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.91,0:48:06.45,中文,,0,0,0,,所以想來拿光碟 同時想請你幫個忙\N{\r外文}Thought I'd pick up my DVD, and, um, I wanted to ask for your help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.25,0:48:09.41,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 應該沒問題\N{\r外文}Sure... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.00,0:48:13.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直過不去的坎是 她為什麼一直沒告訴我\N{\r外文}The thing I keep obsessing about is why she didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.75,0:48:15.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我們向來對彼此毫不隱瞞\N{\r外文}We told each other everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.37,0:48:18.08,中文,,0,0,0,,她是害怕呢 還是羞愧\N{\r外文}Was she afraid or ashamed?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.66,0:48:20.95,中文,,0,0,0,,她有沒有對你提過\N{\r外文}Did she ever give you a hint about any of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.04,0:48:23.62,中文,,0,0,0,,沒有 一個字都沒說過\N{\r外文}No, no, she never said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.70,0:48:27.00,中文,,0,0,0,,老實說 這整件事看起來都不太可能啊\N{\r外文}Honestly, the whole thing seems really just unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.08,0:48:28.91,中文,,0,0,0,,或許這才是她真實的一部分\N{\r外文}Maybe it's a part of who she really was,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.00,0:48:31.49,中文,,0,0,0,,也是她讓我進行這場瘋狂的\N{\r外文}and it's one of the reasons she sent me on this crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.49,0:48:32.79,中文,,0,0,0,,"亞歷克斯夢遊僊境"之旅的原因之一\N{\r外文}"Alex in Wonderland"journey
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.87,0:48:34.58,中文,,0,0,0,,為了讓我自己發現真相\N{\r外文}to find out for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.66,0:48:36.25,中文,,0,0,0,,不要這條 太無聊了 什麼\N{\r外文}-No, way too boring. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.83,0:48:38.50,中文,,0,0,0,,用點心思吧 布拉德利\N{\r外文}Make an effort here, Bradley.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.08,0:48:42.16,中文,,0,0,0,,那麼\N{\r外文}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.04,0:48:44.75,中文,,0,0,0,,願意幫我找約翰尼·阿爾瓦雷斯嗎\N{\r外文}Will you help me find Johnny Alvarez?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.83,0:48:47.54,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 當然 我們可以先用谷歌搜索他\N{\r外文}Yeah, yeah, of course. We could start by googling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.62,0:48:49.50,中文,,0,0,0,,哇喔 真是什麼都給你想到了\N{\r外文}Wow, you really do think of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.58,0:48:52.04,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 機靈鬼 你查到了什麼\N{\r外文}Okay, smarty-pants, what did you come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.12,0:48:54.66,中文,,0,0,0,,一個名叫 約翰尼·阿爾瓦雷斯的樂隊領隊\N{\r外文}A bandleader named Johnny Alvarez,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.66,0:48:56.12,中文,,0,0,0,,可是他是1918年出生的\N{\r外文}except he was born in 1918.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.20,0:48:59.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我試過約翰 胡安 喬納森\N{\r外文}Uh, I tried John, Juan, Jonathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.37,0:49:01.37,中文,,0,0,0,,查到了大概一千條記錄\N{\r外文}There's, like, a thousand entries.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.79,0:49:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,完美 正適合你參加初中畢業典禮\N{\r外文}Perfect... for your middle school graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.79,0:49:09.20,中文,,0,0,0,,拜託 這可是去見美麗的蒂娜啊\N{\r外文}Come on, this is the amazing Tina we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.29,0:49:11.70,中文,,0,0,0,,她叫妮娜\N{\r外文}Nina, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.79,0:49:18.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我有一個常合作的做離婚案件的律師 但她收費不低\N{\r外文}Um, there is someone that I use on divorce cases, but she's not cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.62,0:49:22.70,中文,,0,0,0,,如果是錢的問題 我可以跟 不是錢的問題\N{\r外文}-If the money's a problem, I can talk- No, it's not the money. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.41,0:49:27.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我現在面對的情況非常複雜\N{\r外文}It's like I've fallen down this weird rabbit hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.58,0:49:30.62,中文,,0,0,0,,多年前的家族秘密 私家偵探\N{\r外文}Old family secrets, private detectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.45,0:49:32.87,中文,,0,0,0,,還跟一個律師成了朋友\N{\r外文}becoming friends with a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.54,0:49:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都亂套了\N{\r外文}Nothing makes sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.08,0:49:36.58,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我們現在是朋友了\N{\r外文}So we're friends now?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.16,0:49:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,看起來不錯\N{\r外文}Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.08,0:49:47.25,中文,,0,0,0,,是嗎 是的\N{\r外文}-Yeah? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.33,0:49:49.41,中文,,0,0,0,,接下來你就只缺一套相配的西裝了\N{\r外文}Now all you need is a suit to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.00,0:49:51.04,中文,,0,0,0,,其實我打算\N{\r外文}I was actually just--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.12,0:49:52.54,中文,,0,0,0,,噓\N{\r外文}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.62,0:49:54.04,中文,,0,0,0,,買一套新西裝 對\N{\r外文}-Get a new suit. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.20,0:50:00.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 小豆子\N{\r外文}Hiya, Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.58,0:50:05.00,中文,,0,0,0,,喜歡我新買的攝像機三腳架嗎\N{\r外文}You like my new tripod stick thingy I got for the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.08,0:50:07.79,中文,,0,0,0,,還不錯 只是有點晃\N{\r外文}It's not bad, just a little shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.87,0:50:09.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我們的椅子\N{\r外文}Our chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.04,0:50:11.66,中文,,0,0,0,,需要打理一下\N{\r外文}Hmm. Needs a little love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.25,0:50:18.16,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 又多了件要操心的事 趕在我\N{\r外文}Well, I'll have to get that taken care of before I...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.37,0:50:27.83,中文,,0,0,0,,趕在我 為什麼說"死"字就什麼難呢\N{\r外文}Before I... Why is it so hard to say "die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.33,0:50:31.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我要死了\N{\r外文}I'm gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.33,0:50:34.66,中文,,0,0,0,,那句話怎麼說來著\N{\r外文}How does that line go?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.95,0:50:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,"當我們擺脫這具朽腐皮囊後 在那死的睡眠中 要做什麼夢"\N{\r外文}"What dreams may come when we shuffle off the mortal coil must..."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.75,0:50:43.79,中文,,0,0,0,,"才能不使我們躊躇顧慮""躊躇顧慮"\N{\r外文}-"...must give us pause.""...give us pause."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.87,0:50:47.66,中文,,0,0,0,,"才能不使我們躊躇顧慮"聽起來挺不錯的\N{\r外文}"...must give us pause."Ah, that's got a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.16,0:50:52.66,中文,,0,0,0,,就好像我可以留在人間 只不過是以一種夢境的狀態\N{\r外文}Like I could stick around, but in some cool dream state
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.75,0:50:54.62,中文,,0,0,0,,沒有疼痛與折磨\N{\r外文}without pain or suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.04,0:51:00.79,中文,,0,0,0,,說起折磨 這本書真他娘太長了吧\N{\r外文}Speaking of suffering, how friggin' long is this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.54,0:51:05.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直在尋找 這本書與清單之間是否存在著\N{\r外文}I just kept looking for some sort of inspiring connection
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.91,0:51:08.45,中文,,0,0,0,,某種發人深省的聯繫\N{\r外文}between the book and the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.00,0:51:10.95,中文,,0,0,0,,但我絞盡腦汁 只能想到\N{\r外文}But the best I could come up with was,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.04,0:51:14.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我是亞哈 你是我的鯨魚\N{\r外文}I'm Ahab, you're my whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.16,0:51:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我讓你開始了這段無望的旅程\N{\r外文}and I've set you off on this hopeless quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.08,0:51:21.91,中文,,0,0,0,,唉 我的膽子真大\N{\r外文}I mean, I got a lot of nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.00,0:51:23.83,中文,,0,0,0,,不 媽媽 你有 對吧\N{\r外文}-No, Mom, you have- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.41,0:51:26.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我這是在做什麼 扮演上帝嗎\N{\r外文}What am I doing? Playing God?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.83,0:51:30.62,中文,,0,0,0,,就好像我是智慧與美德的楷模\N{\r外文}As if I'm some kind of paragon of...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.08,0:51:36.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我向你保證 親愛的 我不是\N{\r外文}wisdom and virtue, which I can assure you, my darling, that I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.62,0:51:38.91,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 那個\N{\r外文}Yeah, so, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.37,0:51:41.37,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸告訴我了\N{\r外文}Dad told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.00,0:51:44.00,中文,,0,0,0,,事實是 我\N{\r外文}The truth is, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.16,0:51:46.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我\N{\r外文}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.58,0:51:54.12,中文,,0,0,0,,事實是我今天早上醒來 我說服了自己\N{\r外文}Truth is, I woke up this morning, and I was convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.20,0:51:58.12,中文,,0,0,0,,要將你從這個瘋狂的任務中解放出來\N{\r外文}that I should release you from this lunatic mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.58,0:52:01.29,中文,,0,0,0,,可我又看了一遍清單\N{\r外文}But then I looked at the list again,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.37,0:52:05.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我認真地跟你說 我知道你寫這個的時候只有13歲\N{\r外文}and I'm telling you, I know you were only 13 when you wrote it...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.45,0:52:07.58,中文,,0,0,0,,但這是一張地圖\N{\r外文}but it is a map
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.33,0:52:11.00,中文,,0,0,0,,用來找尋你最好的自己 你明白我的意思嗎\N{\r外文}toward your best self. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.70,0:52:17.25,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你很掙扎 如果你覺得自己很失敗\N{\r外文}I just... I wanna say, if you're struggling, or if you're feeling like a failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.33,0:52:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,那也沒關係\N{\r外文}it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.29,0:52:22.33,中文,,0,0,0,,尋求幫助並不丟臉\N{\r外文}There's no shame in asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.16,0:52:27.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我現在一天比一天更能體會到這一點\N{\r外文}I'm learning that now more and more every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.08,0:52:34.37,中文,,0,0,0,,"叫我以實瑪利吧"\N{\r外文}"Call me Ishmael."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.45,0:52:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,最棒的開篇之句之一\N{\r外文}One of the best first lines ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.75,0:52:37.62,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.16,0:52:40.79,中文,,0,0,0,,還記得我以前常說的話嗎"叫我媽媽吧\N{\r外文}Remember how I used to say, "Call me Mommy."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.87,0:52:43.25,中文,,0,0,0,,但要記得打電話給我"\N{\r外文}"But just be sure to call."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.12,0:52:47.20,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我的小豆子\N{\r外文}All right, my Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.37,0:52:49.58,中文,,0,0,0,,下回再見\N{\r外文}Till next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.66,0:52:51.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我愛你 通話結束\N{\r外文}I love ya. Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.79,0:53:23.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我記得你是個非常有才華的學生\N{\r外文}I remember you were a very talented student.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.87,0:53:28.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你很有激情 但可能有點缺乏自律\N{\r外文}You had a lot of heart, but maybe not so much discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.37,0:53:31.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我只想彈"綠日"樂隊 和菲奧娜·艾波的歌\N{\r外文}Hmm. I wanted to play Green Day and Fiona Apple,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.91,0:53:34.45,中文,,0,0,0,,可您逼著我練音階和巴赫\N{\r外文}and you made me do scales and Bach.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.50,0:53:37.62,中文,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼要學《月光》\N{\r外文}So why "Clair de Lune"?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.41,0:53:40.79,中文,,0,0,0,,這是我媽媽的最愛\N{\r外文}It was my mom's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.16,0:53:44.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你的母親是一位很特別的女士\N{\r外文}Your mother was a special lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.25,0:53:48.50,中文,,0,0,0,,聽到她去世的消息 我很難過\N{\r外文}And I was sad to hear about her passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.58,0:53:50.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道您不太收學生了 懷曼女士\N{\r外文}I know you don't take on many students, Ms. Wyman,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.91,0:53:54.79,中文,,0,0,0,,但要是我媽在天有靈 知道我是跟您學的 那將很有意義\N{\r外文}but it would have meant so much to her if she knew I was doing this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.12,0:53:57.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好 三個條件\N{\r外文}All right, three conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.75,0:54:04.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你要準時來上課 每天都要練習 包括音階在內\N{\r外文}-You arrive on time... Mm. ...you practice every day, including scales,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.50,0:54:08.08,中文,,0,0,0,,然後你要在六月的獨奏會上表演\N{\r外文}and you perform in the June recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.12,0:54:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,（幫助他人 作出貢獻）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.45,0:54:13.70,中文,,0,0,0,,（紋身 沒必要 ）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.79,0:54:15.25,中文,,0,0,0,,（在滿月下露營）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.33,0:54:18.62,中文,,0,0,0,,（和一名紐約尼克斯的球員單挑 假動作向左 往右邊突破）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.70,0:54:21.16,中文,,0,0,0,,（學會開車 跳過這條更安全 ）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.58,0:54:36.20,中文,,0,0,0,,（爸爸 我想你 有空就給我打電話 滿滿的愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.87,0:55:03.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我在圖書館裏 看到了一些你可能會感興趣的書\N{\r外文}So I was at the library, and I... I saw some books I thought would interest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.29,0:55:06.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你想用錢收買我 讓我尊重你\N{\r外文}So now you're trying to buy my respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.16,0:55:07.91,中文,,0,0,0,,是借不是買\N{\r外文}More like loan it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.00,0:55:09.83,中文,,0,0,0,,必須在兩周內還回去\N{\r外文}They have to be back in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.79,0:55:14.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你對美術感興趣 所以我找了幾本書\N{\r外文}I know you're interested in art, so, um, I found a couple of books,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.58,0:55:17.58,中文,,0,0,0,,包括這本埃貢·席勒的精彩傳記\N{\r外文}including this amazing biography of Egon Schiele.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.20,0:55:19.62,中文,,0,0,0,,他是 我知道他是誰\N{\r外文}-He's this- I know who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.16,0:55:24.37,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 還有這部電影\N{\r外文}Oh, and this DVD.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.87,0:55:27.54,中文,,0,0,0,,背景設在當代的紐約\N{\r外文}It's based in New York, present day.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.62,0:55:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,大概90分鐘長 扮演哈姆雷特的人非常性感\N{\r外文}It's about 90 minutes, and the actor who plays Hamlet is, like, really hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.66,0:55:33.91,中文,,0,0,0,,看看你喜不喜歡\N{\r外文}so maybe give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.04,0:55:56.87,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 羅斯老師\N{\r外文}Hey, Miss Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.70,0:56:07.70,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.79,0:56:11.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我沒把以斯拉當成一隻貓對待 沒錯 結果真的起了反效果\N{\r外文}Okay, so I didn't pretend that Ezra was a cat, and yes, it totally backfired...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.29,0:56:12.29,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 當然\N{\r外文}Yeah, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.37,0:56:13.20,中文,,0,0,0,,很帥氣嘛\N{\r外文}You look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.29,0:56:16.75,中文,,0,0,0,,不 沒關係 代我向西奧問好 好 再見\N{\r外文}No, no, no, that's fine. Just say hi to Theo from me. Okay, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.33,0:56:18.45,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 對不起\N{\r外文}-Hi. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.54,0:56:20.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你剛才說 我沒把以斯拉當成一隻貓對待\N{\r外文}-You were saying? I didn't pretend Ezra was a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.87,0:56:22.04,中文,,0,0,0,,不 那句之後\N{\r外文}No, no, after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.12,0:56:25.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我好像說了你很帥氣\N{\r外文}Oh. Uh, I think I said, you look nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.50,0:56:27.41,中文,,0,0,0,,就是這句 謝謝 你很\N{\r外文}That was it. Thank you. You look--
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.50,0:56:29.95,中文,,0,0,0,,濕漉漉 憤怒又沮喪 我需要你的幫助\N{\r外文}Wet, angry, and frustrated. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.04,0:56:31.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你後來就沒給我打過電話\N{\r外文}You never called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.50,0:56:32.58,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我本來想打的\N{\r外文}I know, I meant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.87,0:56:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,但後來我家裏發生了 一大堆亂七八糟的事\N{\r外文}But then all this messed up family stuff happened--
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.25,0:56:37.41,中文,,0,0,0,,真是太巧了\N{\r外文}That's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.50,0:56:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,家裏亂七八糟的事是我的專長 我真的很樂意幫忙\N{\r外文}Messed-up family stuff is my speciality, and I really would love to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.33,0:56:46.20,中文,,0,0,0,,只不過 我開會要遲到了 之後我還要出席個活動\N{\r外文}It's just, I'm late for a meeting and I have this thing later, hence,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.29,0:56:47.45,中文,,0,0,0,,所以才穿了燕尾服\N{\r外文}monkey suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.66,0:56:51.41,中文,,0,0,0,,要不你跟我一起去吧\N{\r外文}Hey, why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.50,0:56:52.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我被放了鴿子\N{\r外文}My date canceled,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.66,0:56:56.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我們正好可以談談以斯拉 或其他你想聊的話題\N{\r外文}and we can talk about Ezra or anything you want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.08,0:56:57.83,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 這樣不好吧\N{\r外文}Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.91,0:57:00.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我不適合出席重要場合\N{\r外文}I'm not really the kind of person you want to take to a fancy event.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.91,0:57:01.87,中文,,0,0,0,,誰說的\N{\r外文}Says who?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.08,0:57:07.41,中文,,0,0,0,,好盛大的場面 確實不錯\N{\r外文}This is fantastic. Pretty great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.75,0:57:10.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我的媽 那是帕特裏克·尤因嗎\N{\r外文}Holy shit, is that Patrick Ewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.45,0:57:12.29,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 你喜歡籃球\N{\r外文}Wait, you're into basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.37,0:57:15.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我當年可是 迪特馬斯公園中學校隊的控球後衛呢\N{\r外文}I was the point guard at the Ditmas Park Middle School team.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.16,0:57:18.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我愛尼克斯隊 我得去跟他談談\N{\r外文}I loved the Knicks, and I need to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.04,0:57:21.45,中文,,0,0,0,,說來話長\N{\r外文}It's kind of a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.95,0:57:24.12,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你水平高的話 我可以跟你說\N{\r外文}Which I will tell you if you're very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.79,0:57:27.79,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你水平高的話 我可以幫你介紹認識\N{\r外文}Well, if you're very good, I might just introduce you to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.58,0:57:29.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟他認識\N{\r外文}You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.87,0:57:32.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我去存一下外套 馬上回來\N{\r外文}I'm just gonna check my coat. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.91,0:57:35.75,中文,,0,0,0,,帕特裏克·尤因\N{\r外文}Patrick Ewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.12,0:57:43.29,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝 不客氣\N{\r外文}-Yeah. Thank you. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.41,0:58:00.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎麼沒穿燕尾服\N{\r外文}Aren't you supposed to wear a tux?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.29,0:58:02.62,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎麼沒穿女式禮服\N{\r外文}Aren't you supposed to be wearing a fancy gown?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.70,0:58:04.79,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 別搞這種性別規範\N{\r外文}Oh, don't be so gender normative.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.45,0:58:08.79,中文,,0,0,0,,還好你的領帶挺不錯 很帥氣 律師\N{\r外文}At least you got yourself a nice tie. You look damn good, counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.87,0:58:10.12,中文,,0,0,0,,確實很帥氣 不是嗎\N{\r外文}He does, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.79,0:58:12.54,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 這位是妮娜·凱勒\N{\r外文}Alex, this is Nina Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.62,0:58:14.66,中文,,0,0,0,,妮娜 這是我的客戶 亞歷克斯·羅斯\N{\r外文}-Ah! Nina, this is my client, Alex Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.75,0:58:17.12,中文,,0,0,0,,幸會 妮娜 我聽說了好多關於你的事\N{\r外文}It's so nice to meet you, Nina. I've heard so much about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.20,0:58:20.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我也聽說了你不少事 你可能是布拉德最喜歡的客戶\N{\r外文}Yeah, you too. I think you may be Brad's favorite client.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.50,0:58:24.41,中文,,0,0,0,,妮娜剛得到一份工作邀約 負責市長的可持續曼哈頓計劃\N{\r外文}Nina just got offered a job heading the Mayor's Sustained Manhattan Initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.50,0:58:26.45,中文,,0,0,0,,她要搬回紐約了\N{\r外文}-Wow. Looks like she's moving back to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.54,0:58:29.08,中文,,0,0,0,,"我以為自己已金盆洗手 他們又把我拉了回來"\N{\r外文}"Just when I thought I was out, they pulled me back in."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.16,0:58:30.75,中文,,0,0,0,,祝賀\N{\r外文}Well, congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.83,0:58:33.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎麼跑來了 我真沒想到會在這裏碰到你\N{\r外文}What are you doing here? This is the last place I'd think to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.00,0:58:34.83,中文,,0,0,0,,她是跟我一起來的\N{\r外文}She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.91,0:58:35.95,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r外文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.04,0:58:37.12,中文,,0,0,0,,加勒特\N{\r外文}Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.20,0:58:38.91,中文,,0,0,0,,妮娜 泰勒醫生\N{\r外文}Nina. Dr. Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.00,0:58:40.91,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 你們認識 認識\N{\r外文}-You know each other. ...know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.00,0:58:43.79,中文,,0,0,0,,這一點也不奇怪 加勒特認識的人可多了\N{\r外文}That makes perfect sense. Garrett knows everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.87,0:58:45.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我還以為我很特別呢\N{\r外文}And I thought I was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.29,0:58:49.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你很特別 很久之前我和妮娜有過一次非常糟糕的約會\N{\r外文}And you are special. Nina and I had a disastrous date a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.87,0:58:52.83,中文,,0,0,0,,戀情中 雙方都強勢是不行的\N{\r外文}It's impossible to have two alphas in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.91,0:58:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,總得有一方弱勢一點\N{\r外文}Someone always has to be the beta.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.00,0:58:56.41,中文,,0,0,0,,看來這就是我的地位了\N{\r外文}I guess that's where I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.50,0:59:01.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是那個意思 你擁有女孩都非常癡迷的強勢魅力\N{\r外文}Oh, that's not what I meant. You have all the alpha a girl needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.62,0:59:03.50,中文,,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎 我有強勢魅力\N{\r外文}Oh, did you hear that? I have all of the alpha...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.58,0:59:04.75,中文,,0,0,0,,為你的強勢魅力舉杯\N{\r外文}Cheers to your alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.83,0:59:06.50,中文,,0,0,0,,敬布拉德的強勢魅力 舉杯\N{\r外文}To Brad's alpha. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.58,0:59:09.29,中文,,0,0,0,,好厲害 舉杯 我實在太喜歡了\N{\r外文}Wow. That's... Cheers. I love this so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.37,0:59:13.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我要一杯16年陳的威士忌 謝謝\N{\r外文}I will have, uh, the 16-year-old scotch. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.54,0:59:14.91,中文,,0,0,0,,來的人挺多\N{\r外文}it's quite the turnout we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.00,0:59:17.41,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 是啊 我們辦得挺成功 對吧\N{\r外文}Hey, yeah. Yeah, we did good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.50,0:59:21.20,中文,,0,0,0,,也得感謝你說服律所買了三桌\N{\r外文}Partly thanks to you persuading the firm to buy, what, three tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.29,0:59:23.62,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 比讓我成為合夥人要便宜一點\N{\r外文}Yeah, it was a bit cheaper than making me partner, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.08,0:59:27.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟妮娜在一起了\N{\r外文}So, you and Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.00,0:59:30.62,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 你跟亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Yeah. So, you and Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.70,0:59:32.66,中文,,0,0,0,,她人太好了 臨時幫我頂替一下\N{\r外文}Oh, she was kind enough to step in last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.75,0:59:36.25,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 也對 她確實不像是你通常喜歡的類型\N{\r外文}Yeah, no, that makes sense. She doesn't seem like your usual type.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.41,0:59:38.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我通常喜歡什麼類型\N{\r外文}What's my usual type?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.70,0:59:42.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 那種沒這麼 搶下籃板補籃得分 贏下比賽\N{\r外文}-Oh, I don't know. Someone a little less... Tips in the rebound for the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.29,0:59:43.66,中文,,0,0,0,,然後觀眾們就瘋狂了\N{\r外文}And then the crowd goes nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.75,0:59:44.95,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道她這是在幹嘛\N{\r外文}...whatever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.04,0:59:47.79,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 簡直太精彩了\N{\r外文}Whoa! And it was just epic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.87,0:59:51.66,中文,,0,0,0,,對 沒想到她還有這一面\N{\r外文}Exactly. The thing I didn't know I was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.95,0:59:55.54,中文,,0,0,0,,史上最棒的尼克斯\N{\r外文}-The best Knick ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.62,0:59:58.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你居然要到了 帕特裏克·尤因的電郵地址\N{\r外文}You know, I can't believe you got Patrick Ewing's email.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.20,1:00:02.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我想他只是為了擺脫我才給的\N{\r外文}I think he was just trying to get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.50,1:00:03.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\r外文}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.66,1:00:06.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你絕對是迷住了他\N{\r外文}You totally charmed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.50,1:00:09.16,中文,,0,0,0,,就像你迷住了我一樣\N{\r外文}Like you totally charmed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.08,1:00:15.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡和你聊\N{\r外文}You know, I really like talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.70,1:00:19.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡聽你說話\N{\r外文}And I really like listening to you talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.20,1:00:21.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我也很喜歡跟你聊\N{\r外文}Well, I really like talking to you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.08,1:00:23.29,中文,,0,0,0,,也喜歡聽\N{\r外文}And listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.00,1:00:25.08,中文,,0,0,0,,有時候\N{\r外文}And sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.79,1:00:28.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜歡深深地看著你的眼睛\N{\r外文}I like to look really deep into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.33,1:00:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我們這是在瞪眼比賽嗎\N{\r外文}Are we having a staring competition?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.62,1:00:34.45,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\r外文}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.95,1:00:36.37,中文,,0,0,0,,別讓我分散你的注意力\N{\r外文}Well, don't let me distract you,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.37,1:00:38.91,中文,,0,0,0,,因為我下了決心 要公平公正地取勝 但\N{\r外文}'cause I'm determined to win fair and square, but
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.41,1:00:41.83,中文,,0,0,0,,正式約會一次如何\N{\r外文}how about a proper date?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.95,1:00:44.50,中文,,0,0,0,,但我們是\N{\r外文}Well, what about the fact that we--
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.58,1:00:45.58,中文,,0,0,0,,是同事\N{\r外文}Work together?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.33,1:00:50.45,中文,,0,0,0,,嚴格來說我只不過是顧問罷了\N{\r外文}Technically, I'm a mere consultant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.54,1:00:52.66,中文,,0,0,0,,用"只不過"來形容你就太不恰當了\N{\r外文}There's nothing mere about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.79,1:01:07.91,中文,,0,0,0,,自從地鐵上遇見你 我就一直想這樣\N{\r外文}I've been wanting to do that ever since I saw you on the A Train.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.04,1:01:12.41,中文,,0,0,0,,那約會怎麼說\N{\r外文}So, how about that date?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.91,1:01:14.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你覺得我們這一整晚都在幹嘛呢\N{\r外文}What do you think we've been doing all night?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.54,1:01:16.75,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 好吧\N{\r外文}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.83,1:01:29.08,中文,,0,0,0,,（六月）
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.16,1:01:32.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟盧卡斯一直都很要好\N{\r外文}So, Lucas is my bud, always has been.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.50,1:01:35.95,中文,,0,0,0,,他的妻子叫佐伊 從他們約會起 我倆就成了好朋友\N{\r外文}His wife is Zoe, and we became best friends the minute they started dating.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.04,1:01:39.83,中文,,0,0,0,,朱利安是頭號好兒子 在哥倫比亞大學教法律\N{\r外文}And, uh, Julian is the number one son and teaches law at Columbia.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.91,1:01:41.29,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害\N{\r外文}Wow, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.37,1:01:43.37,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 他也覺得自己厲害\N{\r外文}-Yeah, so is he.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.70,1:01:47.16,中文,,0,0,0,,哎呀 今天我可不該遲到\N{\r外文}Shit, I really didn't want to be late today.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.66,1:01:49.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我們沒遲到\N{\r外文}Look, we're not late.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.54,1:01:52.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你不需要向哥哥 父親或任何人 證明任何事\N{\r外文}You don't have anything to prove to your brothers or your dad or anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.66,1:01:57.66,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\r外文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.75,1:02:01.79,中文,,0,0,0,,對不起 我不是 如果他說要上課\N{\r外文}Sorry. I'm... If he says lecture...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.87,1:02:03.62,中文,,0,0,0,,加勒特很受歡迎啊 沒有 很有意思\N{\r外文}Garrett's a hit. It's fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.25,1:02:05.12,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.62,1:02:06.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我能說件事嗎\N{\r外文}Can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.37,1:02:10.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你看起來不一樣了 是好的那種不一樣\N{\r外文}You look different. In a really good way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.79,1:02:12.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我感覺也不一樣了\N{\r外文}I feel different.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.91,1:02:16.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我覺得跟加勒特有關係\N{\r外文}I mean, Garrett has something to do with it, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.45,1:02:19.66,中文,,0,0,0,,但也是生命清單的功勞 是嗎\N{\r外文}-It's also this life list thing. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.75,1:02:22.45,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 誰知道我能不能全完成呢\N{\r外文}Yeah. Who knows if I'll do it all, but
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.16,1:02:25.58,中文,,0,0,0,,但是否全部完成並不一定是關鍵\N{\r外文}I don't know, I wonder if that's even the point, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.66,1:02:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,那跟爸爸和好呢\N{\r外文}What about make peace with Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.33,1:02:30.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我覺得他只是想 找到一個繼續相處的方式\N{\r外文}I think he just wants to find a way forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.95,1:02:32.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\r外文}I know, I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.25,1:02:37.50,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我必須先找到約翰尼 可是一直找不到\N{\r外文}I need to find out about Johnny first, and we haven't had any luck finding him, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.58,1:02:40.50,中文,,0,0,0,,大家好 你們的桌子準備好了 來吧\N{\r外文}Hi, guys, your table is ready. Come on up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.58,1:02:41.83,中文,,0,0,0,,說起清單\N{\r外文}Speaking of the list,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.91,1:02:45.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你絕對想不到我明天要做什麼\N{\r外文}you will never in a million years believe what I'm doing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.62,1:03:22.54,中文,,0,0,0,,非常棒 很有創意的詮釋\N{\r外文}That was a wonderful, original interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.04,1:03:27.16,中文,,0,0,0,,接下來 亞歷山德拉·羅斯 演奏《月光》\N{\r外文}Next up, Alexandra Rose, playing "Clair de Lune."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.75,1:03:29.25,中文,,0,0,0,,借過 抱歉\N{\r外文}Excuse me. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.33,1:04:26.29,中文,,0,0,0,,（學會彈《月光》 這樣媽媽才能不嘮叨）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.37,1:04:31.20,中文,,0,0,0,,有一年夏天 你和哥哥們弄了個洗車兼檸檬水攤\N{\r外文}Remember the summer when you and your brothers did the combination car wash and lemonade stand,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.29,1:04:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,哥哥們理所當然地認為 賺來的錢都會拿去買遊戲\N{\r外文}and your brothers just assumed the money would go to their video game fund...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.08,1:04:38.83,中文,,0,0,0,,他們在這裏生活期間 我們的重要工作之一就是提供教育\N{\r外文}Education is an important part of how we support our families while they live here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.91,1:04:42.16,中文,,0,0,0,,但你把這些掛得到處都是\N{\r外文}But you hung these everywhere
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.25,1:04:44.25,中文,,0,0,0,,直到他們不得不妥協\N{\r外文}until they finally had to relent,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.33,1:04:46.79,中文,,0,0,0,,把所有的錢都捐給了流浪狗救助機構\N{\r外文}and all the money went to the Humane Society.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.37,1:04:49.66,中文,,0,0,0,,（以斯帖之家慈善活動）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.75,1:04:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,（捐一萬美元 就能與帕特裏克·尤因打球）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.00,1:04:57.00,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 是你嗎\N{\r外文}Oh, you're the one?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.08,1:04:58.70,中文,,0,0,0,,是我 你\N{\r外文}It's me. It's you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.79,1:05:00.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟我單挑 我的天吶\N{\r外文}-It's you and me. Oh my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.58,1:05:02.04,中文,,0,0,0,,準備好了 好了 姑娘\N{\r外文}-Ready? I'm ready for you, girl!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.12,1:05:03.66,中文,,0,0,0,,讓我見識一下 高手\N{\r外文}What you got, hotshot?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.37,1:05:19.66,中文,,0,0,0,,（在人群中狂舞 ）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.66,1:05:23.12,中文,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你沒事吧\N{\r外文}Oh my God! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.29,1:05:26.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是說過不能去人群中狂舞嗎\N{\r外文}I thought I said mosh pits were out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.83,1:05:28.87,中文,,0,0,0,,爽 爽\N{\r外文}-Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.95,1:05:35.12,中文,,0,0,0,,只要別靠近紋身店 或任何交通工具就行\N{\r外文}Just don't go anywhere near a tattoo parlor or any vehicle whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.20,1:05:37.04,中文,,0,0,0,,（學會開車）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.87,1:05:39.33,中文,,0,0,0,,（駕校）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.16,1:05:42.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我在用力了\N{\r外文}I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.50,1:05:44.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 但是 可以嗎\N{\r外文}-I know you're trying, but... Got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.66,1:05:47.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你們給自己寫一封信\N{\r外文}I want you to write a letter from you to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.45,1:05:50.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你做到了 成為了一位好老師\N{\r外文}So here we are. Be a great teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.50,1:05:54.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我看了你給我的那部電影\N{\r外文}I watched that movie that you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.79,1:06:03.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道你是一位好老師\N{\r外文}I always knew you were.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.41,1:06:07.83,中文,,0,0,0,,（為什麼這麼害怕 真正的我）
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.91,1:06:10.29,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你正在看這段錄像\N{\r外文}And if you are actually watching this right now...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.00,1:06:13.87,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 我真為你驕傲\N{\r外文}Alex, I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.37,1:06:24.29,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\r外文}-Hi. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.33,1:06:44.37,中文,,0,0,0,,（找到真愛）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.62,1:07:18.54,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.33,1:07:20.50,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Alex!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.16,1:07:23.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 爸爸\N{\r外文}-Hey! Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.75,1:07:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你跑到這兒來幹嘛呢\N{\r外文}What are you doing in this neck of the woods?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.87,1:07:28.66,中文,,0,0,0,,去和一個工作上的朋友喝杯咖啡\N{\r外文}I was just getting coffee with a... a work friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.75,1:07:29.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\r外文}How about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.04,1:07:32.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我剛在附近開完會 正在等網約車\N{\r外文}I just had a meeting nearby. I'm kind of waiting for my Uber now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.50,1:07:36.04,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我沒怎麼聯繫你\N{\r外文}I'm sorry I haven't been in touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.12,1:07:38.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我理解的\N{\r外文}No, I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.08,1:07:40.41,中文,,0,0,0,,至少我自認為我理解了\N{\r外文}I mean, I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.58,1:07:43.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是需要多一點時間\N{\r外文}I just need a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.66,1:07:44.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\r外文}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.95,1:07:52.16,中文,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你\N{\r外文}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.04,1:08:07.16,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 抱歉 我遲到了\N{\r外文}Hey, sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.25,1:08:09.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你沒遲到 是我早到了《月光》\N{\r外文}You're not. I'm early. Uh,"Clair de Lune."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.87,1:08:12.79,中文,,0,0,0,,搞定九項 還剩三項\N{\r外文}Nine down, three to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.37,1:08:14.29,中文,,0,0,0,,心有靈犀\N{\r外文}Jinx.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.37,1:08:16.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我想讓偵探繼續查下去\N{\r外文}I want to put the detective back on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.20,1:08:20.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你會說 她上次已經查不下去了 而且要花很多錢\N{\r外文}I know, I know you're gonna say she hit a dead end and that it's a lot of money--
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.37,1:08:21.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我已經讓她去查了\N{\r外文}I already did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.87,1:08:26.91,中文,,0,0,0,,錢你可以以後再還我 不還也行\N{\r外文}I know, you can pay me back later or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.00,1:08:29.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你只需要繼續當我的造型師就行\N{\r外文}You could just keep being my stylist. Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.16,1:08:33.54,中文,,0,0,0,,重點是必須找到約翰尼 對吧\N{\r外文}The point is, we have to find Johnny, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.79,1:08:38.75,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\r外文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.41,1:08:40.54,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 不客氣\N{\r外文}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.75,1:08:42.83,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 三明治\N{\r外文}Ooh, sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.70,1:08:46.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟加勒特怎麼樣了\N{\r外文}So how are things with Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.33,1:08:47.37,中文,,0,0,0,,挺好的 非常好\N{\r外文}Good. Really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.91,1:08:48.83,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\r外文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.45,1:08:51.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛這樣看著我\N{\r外文}Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.95,1:08:53.66,中文,,0,0,0,,可能也沒什麼\N{\r外文}It's probably nothing, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.50,1:08:56.91,中文,,0,0,0,,但他從不想來我家過夜 你覺得這樣奇怪嗎\N{\r外文}Do you think it's strange he never wants to stay at my place?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.00,1:09:00.20,中文,,0,0,0,,電影啊 餐廳啊 總是由他選\N{\r外文}Like, he always picks the movie or the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.70,1:09:03.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 就好像我們完全生活在他的世界中\N{\r外文}I don't know, it's kind of like we live entirely in his world
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.20,1:09:05.50,中文,,0,0,0,,而他只是偶爾來看看我\N{\r外文}and only occasionally will he visit mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.58,1:09:06.66,中文,,0,0,0,,對\N{\r外文}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.75,1:09:07.79,中文,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\r外文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.87,1:09:09.58,中文,,0,0,0,,感覺確實有問題\N{\r外文}It doesn't sound like nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.66,1:09:13.75,中文,,0,0,0,,沒看到對方書架上有什麼書 冰箱裏有什麼東西\N{\r外文}Like, how do you really know someone unless you've seen their bookshelves
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.83,1:09:16.37,中文,,0,0,0,,又怎麼能真正瞭解對方呢\N{\r外文}or, like, the crazy shit they keep in their fridge?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.33,1:09:20.50,中文,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們每次談起加勒特 你都會變得怪怪的\N{\r外文}How come every time we talk about Garrett, you get all weird?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.58,1:09:21.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我還以為你們是朋友呢\N{\r外文}I thought you guys were friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.91,1:09:25.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我們是朋友 從某種意義上說\N{\r外文}We are friends. Of a certain kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.08,1:09:26.75,中文,,0,0,0,,互相不喜歡的那種\N{\r外文}The kind that don't really like each other?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.83,1:09:31.37,中文,,0,0,0,,在情況惡化之前 你應該跟他談談\N{\r外文}The point is that you should talk to him about it before it festers.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.16,1:09:33.00,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r外文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.79,1:09:46.54,中文,,0,0,0,,薩金娜是在這兒長大的 但現在在孟買做小額貸款\N{\r外文}Sakina grew up here but works in Mumbai doing microfinancing,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.62,1:09:49.70,中文,,0,0,0,,拉塞爾是精神病研究所的所長\N{\r外文}and Russell is the president of the Psychiatric Institute.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.29,1:09:51.50,中文,,0,0,0,,能拜託你一件事嗎\N{\r外文}Hey, can I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.58,1:09:53.87,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚能不能別提清單的事\N{\r外文}-Uh-huh. Can we not talk about the list tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.95,1:09:55.41,中文,,0,0,0,,為什麼 大家都愛聽這個故事\N{\r外文}Why? Everyone loves that story.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.50,1:09:57.41,中文,,0,0,0,,這不是故事 這是我的人生\N{\r外文}It's not a story, it's my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.50,1:10:00.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我開始覺得 自己像是你的寵物在表演節目\N{\r外文}and I'm starting to feel like a favorite pet trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.79,1:10:04.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 沒問題 不提生命清單\N{\r外文}Yeah, no, of course, sure. No life list.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.75,1:10:06.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\r外文}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.83,1:10:08.87,中文,,0,0,0,,沒事\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.95,1:10:09.79,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.50,1:10:13.00,中文,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 只是\N{\r外文}It's nothing, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.50,1:10:16.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我們為什麼從來不去我家\N{\r外文}How come we never stay at my place?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.41,1:10:19.37,中文,,0,0,0,,比如 去我家做晚飯\N{\r外文}Like, make dinner at my place.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.45,1:10:21.79,中文,,0,0,0,,因為你很喜歡我的公寓啊\N{\r外文}Because you love my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.87,1:10:24.62,中文,,0,0,0,,對 這裏是很棒 只是\N{\r外文}I do, it's amazing, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.12,1:10:25.95,中文,,0,0,0,,這裏是你的\N{\r外文}It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.04,1:10:29.12,中文,,0,0,0,,這是你的生活和你的朋友 還有\N{\r外文}It's your life and your friends and...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.95,1:10:31.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知該怎麼說\N{\r外文}I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.91,1:10:35.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是覺得或許 你也會想成為我生活中重要的一部分\N{\r外文}I thought maybe you'd want to be a bigger part of my life too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.12,1:10:38.00,中文,,0,0,0,,當然 我不是跟你家人聚過嗎 我們\N{\r外文}Yeah, yeah, and we've hung out with your family. We--
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.08,1:10:39.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我們就只吃過一次早午餐\N{\r外文}We had brunch once.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.29,1:10:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你總說我應該更多表達自己的感受\N{\r外文}You always say that I should work harder at unraveling my feelings, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.08,1:10:48.20,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我現在就在表達\N{\r外文}Here they are, unraveled.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.20,1:10:52.33,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 我很抱歉\N{\r外文}Thank you, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.33,1:10:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,對不起 你說得對\N{\r外文}I'm sorry, you're right, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.00,1:10:57.62,中文,,0,0,0,,只是我不太擅長作客 因為我有點控制狂\N{\r外文}I'm a really bad guest 'cause I'm a bit of a control freak.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.66,1:11:00.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我是個很嚴重的控制狂\N{\r外文}I'm a lot of a control freak.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.79,1:11:02.62,中文,,0,0,0,,或許你應該去看看心理醫生\N{\r外文}Maybe you should see a shrink.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.79,1:11:06.66,中文,,0,0,0,,或許我應該去你家過夜\N{\r外文}Well, maybe I should just stay at your place.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.75,1:11:07.95,中文,,0,0,0,,真的嗎\N{\r外文}Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.54,1:11:09.62,中文,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\r外文}Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.70,1:11:20.54,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 等我一下\N{\r外文}Oh, just give me one second.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.62,1:11:25.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 布拉德利\N{\r外文}Hello, Bradley.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.66,1:11:27.75,中文,,0,0,0,,對 怎麼了\N{\r外文}Yeah, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.83,1:11:32.12,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\r外文}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.33,1:11:35.33,中文,,0,0,0,,寶貝 他們找到我爸爸了\N{\r外文}-Baby? They found my dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.91,1:11:37.20,中文,,0,0,0,,他們找到約翰尼了\N{\r外文}They found Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.29,1:11:40.62,中文,,0,0,0,,他在佛蒙特州 還在做音樂 只是換了個名字\N{\r外文}He lives in Vermont, and he's still a musician, just under a different name.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.70,1:11:43.00,中文,,0,0,0,,所以之前才找不到他 太棒了\N{\r外文}-Which is why we couldn't find him. Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.08,1:11:44.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你父親失蹤了\N{\r外文}Your father was missing?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.41,1:11:45.91,中文,,0,0,0,,不是 是的\N{\r外文}No. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.00,1:11:49.00,中文,,0,0,0,,說來話長 但這下我非得告訴你們了\N{\r外文}It's kind of a long story, which I guess now I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.08,1:11:52.00,中文,,0,0,0,,這也沒關係 因為我還沒來得及讀你《紐約客》的文章\N{\r外文}Which is fine because I didn't get a chance to read yourNew Yorkerarticle,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.08,1:11:54.58,中文,,0,0,0,,而且加勒特說 我們不能談梅根·馬克爾的事\N{\r外文}and Garrett says that we can't talk about Meghan Markle.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.62,1:11:57.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 我叫亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Hi, I'm Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.83,1:11:59.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 你好\N{\r外文}-Hi. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.20,1:12:00.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\r外文}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.91,1:12:12.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你們打算怎麼辦\N{\r外文}So, what have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.58,1:12:15.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我和加勒特明天開車去伯靈頓\N{\r外文}Uh, well, Garrett and I are driving up to Burlington tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.08,1:12:18.33,中文,,0,0,0,,去約翰尼樂隊演出的俱樂部找他\N{\r外文}I'm gonna show up at the club where Johnny's band plays and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.41,1:12:20.41,中文,,0,0,0,,這樣會不會太突兀了\N{\r外文}Are you sure that's not, like, too in his face?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.50,1:12:23.29,中文,,0,0,0,,或許吧 但如果我突然打給他 而他拒絕見我\N{\r外文}Maybe, but if I call him out of the blue and he blows me off,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.37,1:12:25.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我可能會受不了\N{\r外文}I don't know if I can handle that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.66,1:12:28.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我得掛了 我的第一位晚餐客人來了\N{\r外文}I gotta go. My first dinner guest has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.70,1:12:30.25,中文,,0,0,0,,有情況跟你說 祝你好運\N{\r外文}-I'll keep you posted. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.33,1:12:32.16,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝 來了\N{\r外文}-Thanks. Coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.83,1:12:37.04,中文,,0,0,0,,看 嘿\N{\r外文}-Ta-da! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.12,1:12:39.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你好嗎 請進\N{\r外文}-How are you? Mwah. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.66,1:12:42.75,中文,,0,0,0,,這裏看起來棒極了 有這麼多新傢俱 感覺很\N{\r外文}Place looks fantastic with all the new furniture. It feels so...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.83,1:12:43.87,中文,,0,0,0,,小\N{\r外文}Small?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.58,1:12:47.20,中文,,0,0,0,,感覺很像你 太可愛了\N{\r外文}It feels so you. So adorable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.29,1:12:48.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你嘴真甜\N{\r外文}You're sweet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.12,1:12:52.04,中文,,0,0,0,,好勒 我把這個拿到廚房去 然後我要換件衣服\N{\r外文}Okay, let me take this to the kitchen and I'll go get changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.16,1:12:54.41,中文,,0,0,0,,就當在自己家 好嗎\N{\r外文}Make yourself at home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.50,1:12:55.83,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝 嗯\N{\r外文}Thank you. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.25,1:13:15.29,中文,,0,0,0,,別坐單人沙發 彈簧得修一下\N{\r外文}Oh, don't sit in the armchair. I have to get the springs fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.37,1:13:17.20,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r外文}-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.29,1:13:18.75,中文,,0,0,0,,幫我開個門好嗎\N{\r外文}Can you get that, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.25,1:13:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你們好\N{\r外文}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.16,1:13:24.20,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 你比亞歷克斯描述的還要帥\N{\r外文}Wow. You're even hotter than Alex said.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.75,1:13:26.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我是梅根 我是\N{\r外文}-I'm Megan. I'm--
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.00,1:13:30.79,中文,,0,0,0,,加勒特 這是我女朋友內爾 亞歷克斯 我們到了\N{\r外文}Garrett, duh. This is my girlfriend, Nell. Alex, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.87,1:13:31.87,中文,,0,0,0,,馬上來\N{\r外文}Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.95,1:13:33.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\r外文}Hey. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.08,1:13:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你好 哇 這地方好小\N{\r外文}-Hi. Wow, this place is tiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.75,1:13:38.45,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道她房租多少\N{\r外文}I wonder what she's paying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.54,1:13:41.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\r外文}Oh. My. God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.91,1:13:44.58,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 你紋身了\N{\r外文}Alex, you got a tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.66,1:13:46.29,中文,,0,0,0,,那是不是 是啊 清單\N{\r外文}-Is that the... Yeah. The list!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.37,1:13:49.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我簡直不敢相信她完成了這麼多\N{\r外文}I can't believe how much she's already done.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.20,1:13:53.29,中文,,0,0,0,,只剩下這個還沒完成\N{\r外文}Oh, except that one still isn't crossed off.
