Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.87,1:20:51.12,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 她工作上有急事\N{\r外文}Oh, uh, she had a work emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.20,1:20:53.66,中文,,0,0,0,,還好她買到了回紐約的航班\N{\r外文}Luckily she was able to get a flight back to New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.37,1:20:55.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\r外文}You good?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.25,1:20:58.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我看起來怎麼樣 這是不是\N{\r外文}How do I look? Is this...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.29,1:21:00.45,中文,,0,0,0,,很不錯\N{\r外文}You look great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.54,1:21:01.41,中文,,0,0,0,,是嗎\N{\r外文}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.41,1:21:03.25,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\r外文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.79,1:21:05.41,中文,,0,0,0,,也謝謝你陪我來\N{\r外文}And for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.54,1:21:09.45,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\r外文}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.04,1:21:11.37,中文,,0,0,0,,一定會很順利的\N{\r外文}This is gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.58,1:21:13.50,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.58,1:21:15.66,中文,,0,0,0,,會很順利的\N{\r外文}It's gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.16,1:21:19.45,中文,,0,0,0,,（遊牧者俱樂部）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.66,1:22:07.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我們還是走吧 不會有好結果\N{\r外文}Let's just go. This is... This is a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.04,1:22:09.62,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 等等 別急\N{\r外文}Hey, wait. Just, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.41,1:22:11.37,中文,,0,0,0,,看著我\N{\r外文}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.50,1:22:13.50,中文,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\r外文}Take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.66,1:22:20.16,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 走過去 跟他聊聊 記住 有我在這裏做你的後盾\N{\r外文}Now, just go over there and talk to him. Remember, I am right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.83,1:22:22.75,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r外文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.58,1:22:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,糟糕\N{\r外文}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.87,1:22:26.91,中文,,0,0,0,,糟糕\N{\r外文}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.70,1:22:28.62,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r外文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.41,1:22:30.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你有手機嗎\N{\r外文}Do you have a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.66,1:22:31.58,中文,,0,0,0,,有\N{\r外文}Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.66,1:22:32.95,中文,,0,0,0,,有嗎 拿出來\N{\r外文}Yeah? Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.04,1:22:33.91,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\r外文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.00,1:22:35.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想幫你們拍張自拍\N{\r外文}I want to take a selfie.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.37,1:22:38.70,中文,,0,0,0,,總比你倆一直盯著我看 要持續得久一點\N{\r外文}It will last way longer than you two staring a hole through my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.79,1:22:39.83,中文,,0,0,0,,對不起 我們\N{\r外文}I'm sorry, we--
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.91,1:22:41.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你們是稅務局的人嗎\N{\r外文}Are you from the revenue?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.83,1:22:45.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我們不是國稅局的人\N{\r外文}It's... Uh... We're not from the IRS.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.70,1:22:49.87,中文,,0,0,0,,其實 我的名字叫布拉德 這位是亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Actually, my name is Brad, and this is Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.45,1:22:54.16,中文,,0,0,0,,全名是亞歷山德拉·羅斯\N{\r外文}Alexandra, actually. Rose.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.75,1:22:57.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\r外文}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.95,1:22:58.83,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷山德拉\N{\r外文}Alexandra.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.08,1:23:00.95,中文,,0,0,0,,驚喜\N{\r外文}Surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.87,1:23:04.00,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷山德拉·卡羅琳娜·羅斯\N{\r外文}Alexandra Carolina Rose.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.87,1:23:06.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我的全名\N{\r外文}You know my full name.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.33,1:23:08.75,中文,,0,0,0,,當然 你出生時 我寫了一首歌\N{\r外文}Of course. I wrote a song when you were born.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.83,1:23:11.45,中文,,0,0,0,,名字叫《一朵別人名下的玫瑰》\N{\r外文}It was called Una Rosa Con El Nombre De Otra.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.54,1:23:13.25,中文,,0,0,0,,是一首悲傷的情歌\N{\r外文}A sad love song.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.08,1:23:15.50,中文,,0,0,0,,關於伊麗莎白和你的\N{\r外文}About Elizabeth and you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.12,1:23:17.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你錄下來了嗎\N{\r外文}Did you ever record that?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.50,1:23:21.58,中文,,0,0,0,,沒有 那只是 我面對生命中那一刻的一種方式\N{\r外文}No. No, no. It was just a way of dealing with life in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.91,1:23:24.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我很好奇 你都喜歡什麼音樂\N{\r外文}So, I'm curious, what kind of music do you like?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.20,1:23:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,各種各樣的\N{\r外文}All kinds.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.66,1:23:31.04,中文,,0,0,0,,最近我一直在聽 一個我很喜歡的墨西哥歌手\N{\r外文}Lately, I've been listening to this Mexican singer I really like,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.12,1:23:32.16,中文,,0,0,0,,娜塔莉亞·拉弗卡德\N{\r外文}Natalia Lafourcade.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.25,1:23:33.37,中文,,0,0,0,,額\N{\r外文}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.45,1:23:36.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我最近一直在上鋼琴課 好一陣子了\N{\r外文}Oh, and I've been taking piano lessons for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.62,1:23:40.41,中文,,0,0,0,,要彈好一樣樂器 需要很大的努力 做任何事都是\N{\r外文}It's a lot of work to get good at an instrument. Or anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.50,1:23:43.66,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 比如說 人生\N{\r外文}Yeah. Life, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.25,1:23:47.70,中文,,0,0,0,,為紀念你美麗的母親 敬一杯\N{\r外文}To the memory of your beautiful mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.16,1:23:50.12,中文,,0,0,0,,碰杯\N{\r外文}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.12,1:23:57.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我能問你一件事嗎\N{\r外文}Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.25,1:24:00.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你有沒有好奇過我的事\N{\r外文}Were you ever curious about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.25,1:24:01.33,中文,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\r外文}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.45,1:24:05.20,中文,,0,0,0,,很久以前 我去紐約演出過\N{\r外文}I played a gig in New York a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.29,1:24:07.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我們在城裏的時候\N{\r外文}And while we were in town, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.20,1:24:11.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我開車去了布魯克林 我把車停在你們家門口\N{\r外文}I drove out to Brooklyn and I parked my car in front of your house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.29,1:24:14.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我看到你的哥哥們放學回來\N{\r外文}I saw your brothers coming back from school
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.83,1:24:19.75,中文,,0,0,0,,塞繆爾按著喇叭 把車停在車道上\N{\r外文}and Sam honking his horn as he pulled into the driveway.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.83,1:24:24.50,中文,,0,0,0,,然後前門打開了\N{\r外文}And then the front door opens and...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.29,1:24:29.08,中文,,0,0,0,,一個小女孩出來 迎接她的爸爸\N{\r外文}a little girl comes out to greet her dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.58,1:24:32.29,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我好像從來沒有那樣過\N{\r外文}No, I don't think I ever did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.37,1:24:37.12,中文,,0,0,0,,他抱起你搖啊搖 然後你倆一起回屋裏去了\N{\r外文}He swings you round and round, and then the two of you go back into the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.70,1:24:38.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不 那是\N{\r外文}No, that...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.08,1:24:42.54,中文,,0,0,0,,塞繆爾從來不會跟我這樣\N{\r外文}That's just not something that Samuel would do with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.04,1:24:48.79,中文,,0,0,0,,或許是因為他不是我真正的父親吧\N{\r外文}Maybe because the fact is he isn't my real father.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.83,1:24:50.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你才是\N{\r外文}You are.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.79,1:24:56.37,中文,,0,0,0,,事實與真相是兩碼事\N{\r外文}There are facts, and there's what's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.25,1:24:59.54,中文,,0,0,0,,這兩樣都很重要\N{\r外文}And a person needs to make room for both.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.16,1:25:05.08,中文,,0,0,0,,他叫什麼名字\N{\r外文}What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.16,1:25:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,布拉德 布拉德\N{\r外文}-Brad. Brad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.00,1:25:10.00,中文,,0,0,0,,布拉德看起來挺不錯 他是你男朋友嗎\N{\r外文}Brad seems like a cool guy. Is he your... your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.08,1:25:11.08,中文,,0,0,0,,不是 不是\N{\r外文}-No. No?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.16,1:25:12.16,中文,,0,0,0,,不 他是\N{\r外文}No, he's, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.75,1:25:15.45,中文,,0,0,0,,他只是一個很棒的朋友\N{\r外文}He's just a really great friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.54,1:25:17.00,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 約翰尼 嗯\N{\r外文}Hey, Johnny. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.58,1:25:18.58,中文,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎\N{\r外文}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.37,1:25:20.75,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 回去工作了\N{\r外文}Yeah. Back to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.83,1:25:23.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 對 當然\N{\r外文}Right, yeah. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.12,1:25:24.08,中文,,0,0,0,,額\N{\r外文}Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.58,1:25:26.87,中文,,0,0,0,,演出結束後 我們能再聊聊嗎\N{\r外文}Can we maybe talk some more after the set?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.95,1:25:30.20,中文,,0,0,0,,可能會有點困難 我們可以明天早上見 如果你想的話\N{\r外文}Uh, that's going to be tricky, but we can meet tomorrow morning if you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.29,1:25:32.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你住在哪裏 櫻桃街上的萬豪酒店\N{\r外文}-Where are you staying? At the Marriott on Cherry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.75,1:25:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,好 他們的咸牛肉土豆餅做得很好吃\N{\r外文}Uh-huh. Yeah, they make a pretty good corned beef hash there, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.04,1:25:39.25,中文,,0,0,0,,早上10點\N{\r外文}Ten in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.41,1:25:43.54,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\r外文}That would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.62,1:25:45.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我們明早見\N{\r外文}I'll see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.70,1:25:46.66,中文,,0,0,0,,再見 亞歷山德拉\N{\r外文}Bye, Alexandra.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.20,1:26:00.16,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎麼樣\N{\r外文}Hey. How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.37,1:27:00.62,中文,,0,0,0,,那感覺挺尷尬的 但與此同時 也很 真實\N{\r外文}I mean, it was awkward, but at the same time, it felt so... real.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.70,1:27:01.91,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 親密\N{\r外文}-Yeah. Intimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.83,1:27:03.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\r外文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.58,1:27:07.58,中文,,0,0,0,,他說話的方式也非常酷 說什麼\N{\r外文}And he has this really cool way of saying things like,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.66,1:27:10.12,中文,,0,0,0,,"事實與真相是兩碼事"\N{\r外文}"There's facts, and there's what's true."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.66,1:27:14.16,中文,,0,0,0,,他還問我們是不是"稅務局的人"\N{\r外文}What about when he asked if we were from "the revenue"?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.25,1:27:15.75,中文,,0,0,0,,他真是個純爺們\N{\r外文}-Yeah. He's such a man's man.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.83,1:27:16.66,中文,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\N{\r外文}I know!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.79,1:27:19.45,中文,,0,0,0,,對了 他還問你是不是我男朋友\N{\r外文}By the way, he asked if you're my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.54,1:27:20.54,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吧 真的\N{\r外文}-No way. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.25,1:27:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我覺得他喜歡你\N{\r外文}I think he liked you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.79,1:27:26.95,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你的意思是 你要搬來佛蒙特州了\N{\r外文}So what you're saying is you're moving to Vermont.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.04,1:27:29.66,中文,,0,0,0,,為什麼不呢 這裏這麼美\N{\r外文}Mm-hmm. I mean, why not? It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.75,1:27:32.75,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 這兒還有奶牛 我可喜歡奶牛了\N{\r外文}-Okay. And there's cows, and I love cows.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.83,1:27:36.91,中文,,0,0,0,,還有冰淇淋 而且我爸爸住在這裏\N{\r外文}And there's ice cream. And my dad lives here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.00,1:27:38.54,中文,,0,0,0,,不 你是個城裏姑娘\N{\r外文}No, you're a city girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.62,1:27:40.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你擠牛奶 開玩笑吧 這可不\N{\r外文}You milking cows? Are you kidding? That's not--
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.91,1:27:43.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我又沒說要來擠牛奶 你瘋了嗎\N{\r外文}I wouldn't be milking the cows. Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.41,1:27:46.83,中文,,0,0,0,,事實與真理是兩碼事\N{\r外文}There's the facts, and then there's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.91,1:27:51.45,中文,,0,0,0,,不 他說的是 事實與真相是兩碼事\N{\r外文}No. No, he said there is facts, and then there's what's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.04,1:27:53.20,中文,,0,0,0,,真相是什麼\N{\r外文}What's true?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.29,1:27:57.25,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 事實 這是一個玻璃杯\N{\r外文}Okay. Fact, this is a glass.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.08,1:27:59.45,中文,,0,0,0,,真理\N{\r外文}-Uh-huh. Truth...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.29,1:28:01.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我們需要再喝一杯\N{\r外文}We need another drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.62,1:28:04.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我們已經放了三首希妮德的歌了 我們必須放希妮德\N{\r外文}We already played three by Sinead. We have to play Sinead.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.41,1:28:08.25,中文,,0,0,0,,能不能稍微來點變化呀 大晚上的 不行\N{\r外文}-Just have some variety in our evening... No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.33,1:28:10.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你把每個按鈕都按了一遍\N{\r外文}You just pressed every single button.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.00,1:28:11.83,中文,,0,0,0,,這下我們沒有\N{\r外文}Now we have no--
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.12,1:28:18.33,中文,,0,0,0,,喲 怎麼回事 你隨便按了幾個數字而已\N{\r外文}Yo! What? You pressed random numbers!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.08,1:28:37.91,中文,,0,0,0,,居然放了我們的歌\N{\r外文}I can't believe our song came on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.33,1:28:43.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你的噓聲比你的說話聲還響\N{\r外文}Your shushing was louder than you were talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.62,1:28:51.08,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\r外文}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.16,1:28:52.00,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\r外文}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.70,1:28:53.70,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 拜託\N{\r外文}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.45,1:28:55.58,中文,,0,0,0,,這是我的房間\N{\r外文}This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.29,1:28:58.62,中文,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\r外文}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.08,1:29:06.08,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\r外文}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.12,1:29:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安 晚安\N{\r外文}-Good night. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.16,1:29:13.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.58,1:29:57.54,中文,,0,0,0,,心有靈犀\N{\r外文}Jinx.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.95,1:30:04.91,中文,,0,0,0,,這太瘋狂了 我們要停下來嗎\N{\r外文}-This is crazy. Should we stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.00,1:30:06.16,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\r外文}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.37,1:30:12.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你是個接吻高手\N{\r外文}You're a really good kisser.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.54,1:30:14.62,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝 你也是\N{\r外文}Thanks. You too.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.12,1:30:19.41,中文,,0,0,0,,或許可以少用點舌頭 這樣有點癢\N{\r外文}Maybe just a little less tongue. Just tickles a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.50,1:30:20.41,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 好\N{\r外文}Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.41,1:30:25.04,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我的舌頭很大 而且還醉得很厲害\N{\r外文}Sorry, I just have a big tongue, and it's really drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.12,1:30:25.95,中文,,0,0,0,,沒關係\N{\r外文}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.29,1:30:32.75,中文,,0,0,0,,知道他們怎麼說大舌頭的人嗎 怎麼說\N{\r外文}-You know what they say about big tongues. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.16,1:30:50.62,中文,,0,0,0,,布拉德利·阿克曼\N{\r外文}Bradley Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.91,1:30:52.79,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.91,1:30:54.91,中文,,0,0,0,,來\N{\r外文}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.66,1:31:58.62,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r外文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.00,1:32:08.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我其實有點猜到他不會來\N{\r外文}Part of me knew he wasn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.12,1:32:09.25,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.45,1:32:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,但我不會哭的\N{\r外文}But I'm not gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.54,1:32:16.16,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你想哭 就哭吧\N{\r外文}Well, you can if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.04,1:32:58.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我真是笨蛋\N{\r外文}The truth is I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.37,1:33:04.33,中文,,0,0,0,,期待一個完全陌生的人 能解決我生命中的一切問題\N{\r外文}Expecting a total stranger to make everything right in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.12,1:33:09.45,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝你陪我來\N{\r外文}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.45,1:33:29.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你總是說得好像你有什麼不對似的\N{\r外文}You always talk like there's something wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.33,1:33:31.41,中文,,0,0,0,,這是胡扯\N{\r外文}It's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.54,1:33:38.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你聰明 漂亮 充滿活力\N{\r外文}You're so smart and beautiful and full of life and...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.66,1:33:42.95,中文,,0,0,0,,每次我看到你 你都讓我眼花繚亂\N{\r外文}Every time I see you, you dazzle me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.83,1:33:47.54,中文,,0,0,0,,如果加勒特和你爸瞎了眼 那這是他們的損失\N{\r外文}And if Garrett and your dad are too blind to see it, then it is their loss,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.62,1:33:49.37,中文,,0,0,0,,但並不一定我們的損失\N{\r外文}but it does not have to be ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.45,1:33:50.83,中文,,0,0,0,,但事實並非如此\N{\r外文}Except it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.12,1:33:53.62,中文,,0,0,0,,昨晚非常棒\N{\r外文}Last night was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.54,1:33:55.91,中文,,0,0,0,,但那是個錯誤\N{\r外文}But it was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.00,1:33:59.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你有個很棒的女朋友 妮娜不是因為工作才回去的\N{\r外文}-You have this amazing girlfriend- Nina didn't go back because of work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.95,1:34:02.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我們吵了一架 分手了\N{\r外文}We got in a fight and broke up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.04,1:34:07.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你們為什麼吵架\N{\r外文}What was the fight about?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.95,1:34:09.83,中文,,0,0,0,,因為你\N{\r外文}You.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.75,1:34:14.70,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你為什麼不在跟我上床之前告訴我\N{\r外文}Okay. Why didn't you tell me this before you got into bed with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.79,1:34:16.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 我應該說的\N{\r外文}I know I should have.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.20,1:34:20.50,中文,,0,0,0,,對 一切都發生得太快了\N{\r外文}-Yeah. Everything just happened so fast, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.33,1:34:27.58,中文,,0,0,0,,額\N{\r外文}Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.16,1:34:29.50,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.50,1:34:32.33,中文,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\r外文}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.91,1:34:37.33,中文,,0,0,0,,別走 求你了 亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Don't go. Please, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.16,1:34:45.54,中文,,0,0,0,,加勒特是個好男人\N{\r外文}Look, Garrett is an amazing guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.41,1:34:48.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我明白 他\N{\r外文}I get it. He's...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.20,1:34:53.79,中文,,0,0,0,,很成熟又有成就 而且他 我\N{\r外文}sophisticated and accomplished, and he... I...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.54,1:35:00.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我不相信你愛他\N{\r外文}I don't believe you love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.66,1:35:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我甚至都不覺得你喜歡他\N{\r外文}I don't even really think you like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.25,1:35:04.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你喜歡的是 別說了\N{\r外文}-You like how you feel about yourself... You need to stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.83,1:35:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,跟他在一起時對自己的感覺 真的別說了\N{\r外文}-When you're with him. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.08,1:35:09.08,中文,,0,0,0,,自從你媽媽去世後 儘管你已經做了這麼多事\N{\r外文}You need validation even after everything you've done...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.16,1:35:11.16,中文,,0,0,0,,卻還是需要別人的認可 你滿嘴胡話\N{\r外文}-You're full of shit. ...since your mom died.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.25,1:35:13.41,中文,,0,0,0,,要你來教育我要怎麼過我的生活\N{\r外文}Telling me what I want and how to live my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.50,1:35:16.54,中文,,0,0,0,,確實輪不到我 這是加勒特的職責\N{\r外文}Right, 'cause that would be Garrett's job.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.50,1:35:21.41,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\r外文}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.62,1:35:51.58,中文,,0,0,0,,沒事\N{\r外文}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.54,1:36:04.79,中文,,0,0,0,,那天晚上不是因為清單\N{\r外文}The other night wasn't about the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.37,1:36:09.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我是因為壞的單人沙發而抓狂 還有你那些朋友\N{\r外文}I was just freaking out about the broken armchair, and your friends were...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.83,1:36:14.45,中文,,0,0,0,,還有我給你的書 你並沒有讀\N{\r外文}And the book I gave you that you didn't read.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.00,1:36:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,但後來\N{\r外文}But then...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.50,1:36:22.33,中文,,0,0,0,,這整個週末 我一直在想你\N{\r外文}I have just spent the whole weekend missing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.75,1:36:26.33,中文,,0,0,0,,想念你的笑容\N{\r外文}I spent the whole weekend missing your smile
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.41,1:36:29.83,中文,,0,0,0,,想念你那些傻里傻氣的東西\N{\r外文}and missing all your goofy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.08,1:36:34.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我意識到我們能好好在一起 我能跟你走下去\N{\r外文}And I realized that we can do this. That I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.62,1:36:39.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你都沒問約翰尼的事怎麼樣了\N{\r外文}You didn't ask me how it went with Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.16,1:36:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,對不起 還 還順利嗎\N{\r外文}I'm so I'm sorry. How... How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.87,1:36:46.87,中文,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\r外文}Not great.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.66,1:36:50.66,中文,,0,0,0,,問題是\N{\r外文}The thing is,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.91,1:36:56.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我亂糟糟的地方 我的朋友們 我讀的書\N{\r外文}my messy place, my friends, the books I read...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.62,1:36:58.70,中文,,0,0,0,,那都是我 加勒特\N{\r外文}They're me, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.00,1:37:03.04,中文,,0,0,0,,全都是我\N{\r外文}They're all me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.70,1:37:37.79,中文,,0,0,0,,（《美國殭屍 血腥末日》 你準備好了嗎 ）
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.75,1:37:44.33,中文,,0,0,0,,（現已上市）
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.41,1:38:11.62,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r外文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.70,1:38:12.70,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r外文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.91,1:38:14.91,中文,,0,0,0,,進去吧\N{\r外文}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.16,1:38:18.12,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.91,1:38:23.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白為什麼 盧卡斯要我們見房產經紀\N{\r外文}I don't understand why Lucas wants us to meet with a broker.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.70,1:38:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我們要等到新年後 才能把房子掛上市呢\N{\r外文}We can't put the house on the market until the new year.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.83,1:38:35.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不介意我問一下吧 你最近怎麼樣\N{\r外文}If you don't mind me asking, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.33,1:38:39.04,中文,,0,0,0,,挺好的 你呢 孩子們怎麼樣\N{\r外文}Good. How are you? How are the kids?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.58,1:38:40.58,中文,,0,0,0,,他們很想你\N{\r外文}They miss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.33,1:38:42.20,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 我也是\N{\r外文}Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.20,1:38:46.41,中文,,0,0,0,,盧卡斯什麼時候到 我還有事要做呢\N{\r外文}When is Lucas getting here? I have stuff to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.50,1:38:48.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我在這裏\N{\r外文}I'm here! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.58,1:38:51.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你們還好嗎\N{\r外文}Hi, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.79,1:38:53.83,中文,,0,0,0,,房產經紀呢 不來了\N{\r外文}-Where's the broker? Broker's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.91,1:38:54.87,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\r外文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.95,1:38:56.95,中文,,0,0,0,,對 我有樣東西想讓你們看\N{\r外文}Yeah, I've got something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.54,1:38:59.62,中文,,0,0,0,,這邊 沒事的 那個\N{\r外文}Just, it's gonna be all right, just...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.83,1:39:04.08,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 我不明白\N{\r外文}Whoa, what? I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.25,1:39:07.12,中文,,0,0,0,,在滿月下露營\N{\r外文}Camping out under a full moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.20,1:39:08.91,中文,,0,0,0,,清單上的第七項\N{\r外文}Number seven on the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.00,1:39:10.04,中文,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\r外文}Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.12,1:39:11.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你有心了 但是 不 克洛伊\N{\r外文}-This is sweet but... No, Chloe--
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.66,1:39:15.33,中文,,0,0,0,,閉嘴 你們兩個都閉嘴 好嗎\N{\r外文}Guys, just stop. Just shut up. Both of you shut up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.41,1:39:18.45,中文,,0,0,0,,這件事我們做定了 所以\N{\r外文}We are gonna do this so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.95,1:39:23.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我們開瓶紅酒 準備開始吧\N{\r外文}Let's crack open the wine, get started.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.50,1:39:25.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好嗎\N{\r外文}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.58,1:39:28.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.58,1:39:32.00,中文,,0,0,0,,於是我10點到了那兒 然後\N{\r外文}So I got there at 10, and
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.58,1:39:34.50,中文,,0,0,0,,半小時過去了 一小時過去了\N{\r外文}half an hour went by, and then an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.58,1:39:37.08,中文,,0,0,0,,約翰尼一直沒出現 你就這樣坐在那裏等\N{\r外文}And Johnny never showed up, and you're just sitting there waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.95,1:39:40.33,中文,,0,0,0,,一定很痛苦吧 亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Must've been so tough, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.29,1:39:42.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我很遺憾\N{\r外文}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.37,1:39:43.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我並不驚訝\N{\r外文}I wasn't totally surprised.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.91,1:39:45.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我挺喜歡他的\N{\r外文}I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.25,1:39:50.20,中文,,0,0,0,,儘管他跟我說的話中透露出\N{\r外文}But even though he told me stuff, it kind of felt like he was
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.29,1:39:52.45,中文,,0,0,0,,他好像有所隱瞞\N{\r外文}-holding something back, you know? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.54,1:39:55.58,中文,,0,0,0,,回來之後 你給爸爸打過電話嗎\N{\r外文}Have you called Dad? Since you-you got back?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.91,1:40:00.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我明白 你還沒準備好 但\N{\r外文}I mean, I-I get it. You're not... You're not ready, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.79,1:40:03.62,中文,,0,0,0,,他整天就知道問你的事\N{\r外文}All he does is ask about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.33,1:40:08.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你之前說 知道了約翰尼的事\N{\r外文}Remember when you said that finding out about Johnny
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.75,1:40:11.04,中文,,0,0,0,,才明白難怪自己和爸爸的關係會這樣\N{\r外文}explained a lot about your relationship with Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.54,1:40:14.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我也有同感\N{\r外文}I felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.04,1:40:18.29,中文,,0,0,0,,只不過對我來說 是你跟媽媽\N{\r外文}Except for me, it was you and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.16,1:40:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你們之間特殊的感情\N{\r外文}Your bond.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.58,1:40:25.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你們的小秘密 你們的私人笑話\N{\r外文}Your little secrets and your private jokes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.75,1:40:29.58,中文,,0,0,0,,就像是一個 我們其他人禁止入內的俱樂部\N{\r外文}Like a club the rest of us weren't allowed into.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.66,1:40:36.83,中文,,0,0,0,,或許你可以想一想 爸爸對此會有怎樣的感受\N{\r外文}Maybe for a moment think about what that was like for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.04,1:40:39.12,中文,,0,0,0,,還有盧卡斯跟我\N{\r外文}For Lucas and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.50,1:40:44.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你也有這種感覺嗎\N{\r外文}Is that how you felt?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.54,1:40:49.54,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\r外文}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.91,1:40:51.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我之前\N{\r外文}I had...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.87,1:40:54.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我之前完全沒意識到\N{\r外文}I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.83,1:41:03.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我得再喝一杯\N{\r外文}I think I need another drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.91,1:41:07.91,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\r外文}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.50,1:41:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我想起了一件事來\N{\r外文}I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.04,1:41:22.58,中文,,0,0,0,,朱利安 我們上來這兒幹什麼啊\N{\r外文}Uh... Julian, what are we doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.66,1:41:24.70,中文,,0,0,0,,對了\N{\r外文}Uh... Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.45,1:41:26.91,中文,,0,0,0,,這邊是什麼\N{\r外文}It's over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.00,1:41:29.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我們最後一次一起上來時什麼時候\N{\r外文}When's the last time we were all up here together?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.54,1:41:30.41,中文,,0,0,0,,猴年馬月了\N{\r外文}Ages.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.12,1:41:32.20,中文,,0,0,0,,不可思議\N{\r外文}Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.29,1:41:34.66,中文,,0,0,0,,還在這裏\N{\r外文}It's still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.37,1:41:39.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天 大哥 搞什麼\N{\r外文}-Oh my God, dude. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.41,1:41:43.33,中文,,0,0,0,,朱利安 你這個小惡魔 這麼久以來你一個字都沒提過\N{\r外文}Julian, you little devil. This whole time you never said anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.41,1:41:46.87,中文,,0,0,0,,即便是書獃子天才 有時候也需要放鬆一下的 好嗎\N{\r外文}Look, even anal brainiacs need to unwind sometimes. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.50,1:41:48.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你們覺得還能抽嗎\N{\r外文}Think it's any good?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.75,1:41:50.87,中文,,0,0,0,,在這兒放了15年了\N{\r外文}It's been here for, like, 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.37,1:41:54.29,中文,,0,0,0,,只有一個辦法能知道了\N{\r外文}Well, there's only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.62,1:42:00.04,中文,,0,0,0,,原來朱利安會上來抽他的秘密藏品\N{\r外文}So, Julian came up here for his secret stash.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.62,1:42:03.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢 盧卡斯 你會來這裏搞什麼小動作\N{\r外文}What about you, Lucas? What shenanigans did you get up to?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.75,1:42:07.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我 我在這裏破了處\N{\r外文}I-I lost my virginity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.16,1:42:10.50,中文,,0,0,0,,就在那個角落 那個床墊上\N{\r外文}in that corner, on that mattress,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.41,1:42:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,跟瓦萊麗·霍夫曼\N{\r外文}with Valerie Hoffman.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.95,1:42:14.70,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 瓦萊麗·霍夫曼\N{\r外文}-Wow! Valerie Hoffman?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.79,1:42:15.83,中文,,0,0,0,,對\N{\r外文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.91,1:42:17.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你根本配不上她\N{\r外文}Dude, she was so out of your league.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.50,1:42:18.54,中文,,0,0,0,,哎 我知道\N{\r外文}Dude, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.62,1:42:19.95,中文,,0,0,0,,額\N{\r外文}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.04,1:42:24.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我也說不好 一次而已 我猜也是\N{\r外文}-I don't know, it was a one-time thing. I bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.25,1:42:29.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我只記得 聽到樓下一直在放《奧普拉脫口秀》\N{\r外文}It was like, all I remember is hearingOprah on the TV downstairs the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.25,1:42:32.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢 妹妹\N{\r外文}What about you, little sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.00,1:42:35.04,中文,,0,0,0,,有什麼秘密告訴我們嗎\N{\r外文}Any secrets we should know about?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.37,1:42:40.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我以前會跟朋友們搞那種 很誇張的過夜派對\N{\r外文}I used to have these really elaborate sleepovers with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.75,1:42:44.29,中文,,0,0,0,,有一天晚上 我們每個人都寫下了\N{\r外文}And there was one night that we each wrote down
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.37,1:42:47.45,中文,,0,0,0,,自己人生中想要做到的事\N{\r外文}all the things that we wanted to accomplish in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.00,1:42:49.58,中文,,0,0,0,,就是那張清單\N{\r外文}Like, the list?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.62,1:42:52.45,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r外文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.04,1:42:55.00,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\r外文}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.75,1:42:57.75,中文,,0,0,0,,於是就有了今天\N{\r外文}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.08,1:43:02.95,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯\N{\r外文}Alex?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.08,1:43:05.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r外文}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.66,1:43:07.66,中文,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼樣的\N{\r外文}What are they like?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.83,1:43:11.50,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽留給你的那些視頻光碟\N{\r外文}The DVDs Mom left you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.83,1:43:28.08,中文,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎 嗯\N{\r外文}-Ready? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.79,1:43:35.37,中文,,0,0,0,,有一年夏天 你和哥哥們弄了個洗車兼檸檬水攤\N{\r外文}Remember the summer when you and your brothers did the combination car wash and lemonade stand,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.45,1:43:39.91,中文,,0,0,0,,哥哥們理所當然地認為 賺來的錢都會拿去買遊戲\N{\r外文}and your brothers assumed that the money would go to their video game fund,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.00,1:43:43.25,中文,,0,0,0,,但你把這些掛得到處都是\N{\r外文}but you hung these everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.33,1:43:45.45,中文,,0,0,0,,直到他們不得不妥協\N{\r外文}...until they finally had to relent,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.54,1:43:48.37,中文,,0,0,0,,把所有的錢都捐給了流浪狗救助機構\N{\r外文}and all the money went to the Humane Society.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.45,1:43:51.58,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼 我不是說過不能去人群中狂舞嗎\N{\r外文}What? I thought I said mosh pits were out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.66,1:43:53.50,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r外文}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.58,1:43:59.33,中文,,0,0,0,,只要別靠近紋身店 或任何交通工具就行\N{\r外文}Just don't go anywhere near a tattoo parlor or any vehicle whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.91,1:44:01.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能過上最好的生活\N{\r外文}I want you to live your best life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.29,1:44:04.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你必須從坑裏爬出來\N{\r外文}You have to get yourself out of this hole that you're in.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.58,1:44:08.87,中文,,0,0,0,,到時我不在了 沒辦法把你挖出來\N{\r外文}I'm not gonna be around to dig you out,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.87,1:44:10.83,中文,,0,0,0,,但我一定會留一把鏟子給你\N{\r外文}but I can sure as hell leave you a shovel.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.83,1:44:14.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你還記得 我們在州北部租的那間小屋嗎\N{\r外文}Do you remember the cottage we rented upstate?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.37,1:44:19.33,中文,,0,0,0,,到了晚上 我們會一起坐在門廊前\N{\r外文}And at night, we would all go sit out on the porch together
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.41,1:44:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,就這樣看月亮 看星星\N{\r外文}and just look at the moon and the stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.58,1:44:30.25,中文,,0,0,0,,那好像是我們唯一 不說話 不取笑 不爭吵的時候\N{\r外文}And it seemed like the only time that we didn't have to talk or tease or argue.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.66,1:44:34.16,中文,,0,0,0,,有時候你會蜷縮起來 躺在你父親的膝上\N{\r外文}And sometimes you'd curl up in your father's lap,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.75,1:44:36.50,中文,,0,0,0,,是那麼的安靜\N{\r外文}and it was just quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.79,1:44:44.29,中文,,0,0,0,,那一刻 能體驗到那種奇妙的感覺\N{\r外文}Just a moment to experience that sense of wonder
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.41,1:44:50.37,中文,,0,0,0,,去思考 去感悟 並感恩我們所擁有的一切\N{\r外文}and reflect and be grateful for all that we have.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.45,1:44:52.41,中文,,0,0,0,,最重要的 是感恩我們擁有彼此\N{\r外文}And most of all, for each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.91,1:44:54.87,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\r外文}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.16,1:44:58.37,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 爸爸\N{\r外文}Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.54,1:45:00.79,中文,,0,0,0,,見到你真好\N{\r外文}So happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.00,1:45:12.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我下班回家 會把車停上車道\N{\r外文}I would pull up in the driveway, home from work...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.75,1:45:17.95,中文,,0,0,0,,跑出家門 我會把你抱起來轉一圈\N{\r外文}...run out of the house, and I'd pick you up and spin you around.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.16,1:45:33.37,中文,,0,0,0,,（十二月）
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.37,1:45:46.79,中文,,0,0,0,,沙利文先生\N{\r外文}Mr. Sullivan!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.87,1:45:49.45,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷山德拉 很高興見到你\N{\r外文}Alexandra. Wonderful to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.25,1:45:52.87,中文,,0,0,0,,儘管你見到我 好像沒那麼高興\N{\r外文}Even if you don't exactly seem thrilled to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.37,1:45:56.66,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉 只是我以為阿克曼先生會來\N{\r外文}Sorry, it's just, I thought Mr. Ackerman would be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.75,1:45:58.45,中文,,0,0,0,,布拉德利讓我替他道個歉\N{\r外文}Bradley sends his regrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.54,1:46:01.95,中文,,0,0,0,,現在他是正式合夥人了 所以更忙了\N{\r外文}Now that he's a full partner, his schedule is more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.50,1:46:04.29,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 你說他是合夥人了\N{\r外文}I'm sorry. Did you say he's a partner?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.37,1:46:06.75,中文,,0,0,0,,他走進我的辦公室 給我下了最後通牒\N{\r外文}He marched into my office and gave me an ultimatum.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.83,1:46:09.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我當時都不知道是該用戒尺打他手心\N{\r外文}I couldn't decide whether to rap him on the knuckles
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.37,1:46:11.12,中文,,0,0,0,,還是該問他怎麼這麼久才來\N{\r外文}or ask what took him so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.66,1:46:13.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜這是給他的\N{\r外文}I assume that's for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.83,1:46:16.83,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 沒什麼 只是條領帶罷了\N{\r外文}Oh. It's nothing. It's just a tie.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.91,1:46:19.91,中文,,0,0,0,,還有一個圍兜 是我們之間的小玩笑\N{\r外文}-Mm. And a bib, just a little joke between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.00,1:46:21.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我會轉交給他的\N{\r外文}I'll make sure he gets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.25,1:46:26.58,中文,,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白提出這個方案時\N{\r外文}So, when Elizabeth proposed this little scheme,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.66,1:46:28.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我告訴她 她瘋了\N{\r外文}I told her she was off her rocker.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.91,1:46:32.04,中文,,0,0,0,,那時我們一致認為 要找布拉德利這樣的人比較好\N{\r外文}That's when we agreed it'd be wise to have someone like Bradley
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.12,1:46:33.75,中文,,0,0,0,,讓他來具體處理\N{\r外文}handle the particulars.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.83,1:46:37.91,中文,,0,0,0,,無論如何 我希望你這一年沒有受太多苦\N{\r外文}In any case, I hope you haven't suffered too much this last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.33,1:46:41.75,中文,,0,0,0,,確實有過一時的困難\N{\r外文}I had my moments. But, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.00,1:46:44.54,中文,,0,0,0,,但我想這也是其中的目的之一\N{\r外文}I guess that was partly the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.70,1:46:47.83,中文,,0,0,0,,問題是 沙利文先生\N{\r外文}The thing is, Mr. Sullivan, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.45,1:46:51.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我沒能完成清單\N{\r外文}I didn't finish the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.83,1:46:57.91,中文,,0,0,0,,看來真愛一直在躲避我\N{\r外文}Seems true love continues to elude me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.00,1:46:59.91,中文,,0,0,0,,真愛太難搞了\N{\r外文}True love is a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.66,1:47:03.79,中文,,0,0,0,,隨便問問我任何一位前妻\N{\r外文}Ask any of my ex-wives.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.41,1:47:06.66,中文,,0,0,0,,有什麼安慰獎嗎\N{\r外文}Is there like a consolation prize?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.20,1:47:08.20,中文,,0,0,0,,去地中海俱樂部待一周\N{\r外文}A week at Club Med?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.79,1:47:10.54,中文,,0,0,0,,恐怕沒有 嗯\N{\r外文}-I'm afraid not. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.45,1:47:12.45,中文,,0,0,0,,只有這個\N{\r外文}Just this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.58,1:47:18.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你母親覺得這樣不公平\N{\r外文}Your mother didn't think it was fair
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.37,1:47:21.91,中文,,0,0,0,,不能要求你 在這麼短的時間內找到真愛\N{\r外文}to expect you to find true love with a ticking clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.00,1:47:25.37,中文,,0,0,0,,她的原話是 "我希望她不要將就"\N{\r外文}And I quote, "I just hope she won't settle for less."
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.58,1:47:29.54,中文,,0,0,0,,這是你的遺產 親愛的\N{\r外文}Your inheritance, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.25,1:47:33.54,中文,,0,0,0,,（亞歷山德拉）
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.29,1:47:54.54,中文,,0,0,0,,這棟房子\N{\r外文}The house?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.62,1:47:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,這是她自始至終的願望\N{\r外文}Her wish from the start.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.87,1:47:59.75,中文,,0,0,0,,何必這麼大費周章呢\N{\r外文}Why we had to go through the theatrics...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.04,1:48:02.58,中文,,0,0,0,,還有設立了一個小額信託\N{\r外文}There's a small trust
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.66,1:48:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,幫助支付稅款和維護費用 如果你還沒準備好搬進去\N{\r外文}to help cover taxes and maintenance, and if you're not ready to move in,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.20,1:48:08.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以先租出去 直到你準備好\N{\r外文}you can rent it out until you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.87,1:48:10.79,中文,,0,0,0,,完全由你自己決定\N{\r外文}Entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.33,1:48:14.37,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 親愛的 你哭了\N{\r外文}-Oh dear. You're crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.45,1:48:16.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我不擅長哭\N{\r外文}I'm not good at crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.70,1:48:19.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我去叫我的助理來\N{\r外文}Let me get my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.16,1:48:48.00,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r外文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.50,1:48:54.37,中文,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯 親愛的\N{\r外文}Alex, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.00,1:48:55.83,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\r外文}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.58,1:48:59.12,中文,,0,0,0,,終於來了 你成功了\N{\r外文}Here we are. You did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.41,1:49:01.25,中文,,0,0,0,,就差一點\N{\r外文}Barely.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.33,1:49:02.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我從沒懷疑過你\N{\r外文}I never doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.20,1:49:07.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我想跟你說 能做你媽媽\N{\r外文}I want to say that being your mom
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.04,1:49:11.00,中文,,0,0,0,,一直是我生命中最快樂的事\N{\r外文}has been the joy of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.50,1:49:14.08,中文,,0,0,0,,現在 你有了一個新的開始\N{\r外文}And now you're at a new beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.16,1:49:18.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我不會再纏著你了 沒有清單和最後通牒了\N{\r外文}And I will not be haunting you anymore. No more lists and ultimatums.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.58,1:49:21.58,中文,,0,0,0,,你能行\N{\r外文}You got this.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.95,1:49:26.54,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 讓我再說一件事\N{\r外文}So there may be just one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.79,1:49:31.79,中文,,0,0,0,,人生是美好的 凌亂又複雜\N{\r外文}Life is beautiful and messy and complicated,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.87,1:49:35.33,中文,,0,0,0,,有時候看起來不像 你認為它應該有的樣子\N{\r外文}and sometimes it doesn't look the way you think it's supposed to look,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.41,1:49:36.95,中文,,0,0,0,,那也沒關係\N{\r外文}and that is okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.62,1:49:42.12,中文,,0,0,0,,繼續前進 要一直勇敢下去\N{\r外文}Keep going and always be brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.20,1:49:44.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我會的\N{\r外文}I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.25,1:49:46.29,中文,,0,0,0,,至於真愛\N{\r外文}And as for true love,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.12,1:49:50.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我承認 我自己都一直沒搞明白\N{\r外文}I'll admit I never really figured that one out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.83,1:49:52.25,中文,,0,0,0,,但我知道這一點\N{\r外文}But I do know this.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.58,1:49:55.37,中文,,0,0,0,,愛是值得為之奮鬥的\N{\r外文}Love is worth fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.95,1:49:58.87,中文,,0,0,0,,明白嗎\N{\r外文}Understood?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.95,1:50:02.20,中文,,0,0,0,,媽媽 嗨\N{\r外文}-Hey, Mom. Hi!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.29,1:50:03.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我給你泡了茶\N{\r外文}I made you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.58,1:50:04.95,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 親愛的 謝謝\N{\r外文}Oh honey. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.04,1:50:05.91,中文,,0,0,0,,不客氣\N{\r外文}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.66,1:50:11.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你拿這個做什麼啊 我在做一個小項目\N{\r外文}-What are you doing with that? I am doing a little project.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.00,1:50:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,到時候你就知道了\N{\r外文}You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.33,1:50:23.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我好愛你 小豆子 永遠愛你\N{\r外文}I love you so much, Bean. Forever and always.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.62,1:50:25.58,中文,,0,0,0,,別忘了\N{\r外文}Don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.12,1:50:27.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我也愛你 媽媽\N{\r外文}I love you too, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.04,1:50:34.91,中文,,0,0,0,,再見\N{\r外文}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.75,1:51:06.79,中文,,0,0,0,,哎呀\N{\r外文}Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.25,1:51:26.66,中文,,0,0,0,,佐伊 真愛四問題是什麼來著\N{\r外文}Zoe, what are the four true love questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.95,1:51:29.79,中文,,0,0,0,,哎呀\N{\r外文}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.87,1:51:31.54,中文,,0,0,0,,（《白鯨記》）
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.33,1:51:51.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼\N{\r外文}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.62,1:51:53.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你看我像在幹什麼\N{\r外文}What does it look like I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.37,1:51:58.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不接我的電話 我想跟你道歉\N{\r外文}Why didn't you answer any of my calls? I was trying to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.54,1:52:00.54,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我接受道歉\N{\r外文}Okay, well, apology accepted,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.62,1:52:03.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我也很抱歉 但你沒必要撞我的車啊\N{\r外文}and I'm sorry too, but you didn't have to hit my car.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.95,1:52:07.16,中文,,0,0,0,,能進去嗎 我要跟你談談 這樣不好吧\N{\r外文}-Can we go inside? Please, I need to talk. I don't think that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.25,1:52:10.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我們之間發生了這麼多事\N{\r外文}-But- I really don't think it's a good idea
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.12,1:52:13.54,中文,,0,0,0,,還是不要這樣比較好 對不起\N{\r外文}with everything that's happened between us. I'm sorry, but
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.62,1:52:15.70,中文,,0,0,0,,但要和好 然後重新做朋友\N{\r外文}making up and being friends again?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.75,1:52:17.75,中文,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的\N{\r外文}It's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.83,1:52:20.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我可沒說想重新做朋友\N{\r外文}But I didn't say that I wanted us to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.20,1:52:24.00,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 就這麼定了\N{\r外文}Okay, that settles that.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.08,1:52:25.08,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\r外文}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.91,1:52:27.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望我們更進一步\N{\r外文}I want us to be more.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.66,1:52:31.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不只是朋友\N{\r外文}Like, a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.41,1:52:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我上次見你時 你可不是這麼想的\N{\r外文}You didn't the last time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.12,1:52:43.45,中文,,0,0,0,,或許我當時是想的 我只是太困惑了 自己都不知道\N{\r外文}Maybe I did, but I was just too confused to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.54,1:52:48.66,中文,,0,0,0,,也許我只是需要 問自己幾個重要的問題\N{\r外文}and maybe I just needed to ask myself a few important questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.62,1:52:52.79,中文,,0,0,0,,確切地說 是四個\N{\r外文}Um, four, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.87,1:52:54.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你還寫下來了\N{\r外文}You wrote them down?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.29,1:52:58.29,中文,,0,0,0,,"第一 他善良嗎""他"指的是你\N{\r外文}"One. Is he kind?"Meaning you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.33,1:53:01.70,中文,,0,0,0,,毫無疑問 你善良得像一隻小狗\N{\r外文}No question. You're like a puppy dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.45,1:53:04.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟拉布拉多獵犬沒區別\N{\r外文}You might as well be a Labrador Retriever.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.45,1:53:06.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我小時候養過一隻拉布\N{\r外文}I had a lab when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.41,1:53:09.45,中文,,0,0,0,,"第二 我能否把 心中所想的一切都告訴他"\N{\r外文}"Two, can I tell him everything in my heart?"
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.87,1:53:12.87,中文,,0,0,0,,當然能了\N{\r外文}Well, duh.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.75,1:53:18.16,中文,,0,0,0,,自從我們認識那天起 我就一直毫無保留地告訴你一切\N{\r外文}I've been telling you everything pretty much uncensored since the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.87,1:53:24.70,中文,,0,0,0,,"第三 他會幫我成為最好的自己嗎"\N{\r外文}"Three. Does he help me become the best version of myself?"
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.00,1:53:29.33,中文,,0,0,0,,這還用說嗎\N{\r外文}Well, that's a no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.20,1:53:33.12,中文,,0,0,0,,過去的這一年\N{\r外文}I mean, do you think that there's any chance that
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.83,1:53:36.66,中文,,0,0,0,,如果沒有你 我能熬得過來嗎\N{\r外文}I would have gotten through the last year without you?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.20,1:53:40.16,中文,,0,0,0,,沒有你的話\N{\r外文}Done any of it...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.50,1:53:43.45,中文,,0,0,0,,能完成一件嗎\N{\r外文}without you?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.12,1:53:48.37,中文,,0,0,0,,那第四個問題呢\N{\r外文}And the fourth one?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.45,1:53:49.54,中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\r外文}Oh. Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.20,1:53:52.20,中文,,0,0,0,,不重要了\N{\r外文}Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.58,1:53:57.00,中文,,0,0,0,,重要的是 答案是肯定的 所以沒問題了\N{\r外文}The important thing is the answer is yes, so there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.70,1:53:58.91,中文,,0,0,0,,四個問題全中\N{\r外文}Four for four.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.16,1:54:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,那現在怎麼辦\N{\r外文}So what happens now?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.70,1:54:15.58,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\r外文}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.29,1:54:17.70,中文,,0,0,0,,他們說的是真的\N{\r外文}It's true what they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.58,1:54:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,資深合夥人確實更擅長接吻\N{\r外文}Senior partners really do kiss better.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.79,1:54:25.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我們各方面都更擅長 各方面\N{\r外文}-We do everything better. Everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.29,1:54:33.12,中文,,0,0,0,,五 四\N{\r外文}Five, four,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.20,1:54:39.33,中文,,0,0,0,,三 二 一 新年快樂\N{\r外文}three, two, one. Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.70,1:54:43.66,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂 布拉德利·阿克曼\N{\r外文}Happy New Year, Bradley Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.75,1:54:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,誰能想到呢\N{\r外文}Who would've thought?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.62,1:54:57.91,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂\N{\r外文}Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.00,1:54:59.37,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂\N{\r外文}Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.45,1:55:01.66,中文,,0,0,0,,喝 你的一生摯愛\N{\r外文}Cheers. Love of your life?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.75,1:55:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,別取笑我了\N{\r外文}Don't embarrass me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.16,1:55:07.66,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂 佐伊\N{\r外文}Happy New Year, Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.75,1:55:09.12,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂 親愛的\N{\r外文}Happy New Year, my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.33,1:55:11.16,中文,,0,0,0,,愛你\N{\r外文}Love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.25,1:55:12.29,中文,,0,0,0,,以斯拉\N{\r外文}Ezra.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.37,1:55:13.66,中文,,0,0,0,,羅斯老師 新年快樂\N{\r外文}-Miss Rose. Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.75,1:55:14.62,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂\N{\r外文}Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.70,1:55:15.87,中文,,0,0,0,,他考上了帕森設計學院\N{\r外文}Parsons, this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.95,1:55:17.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你敢相信嗎\N{\r外文}-No way! Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.45,1:55:19.75,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 你怎麼都沒告訴我\N{\r外文}-Yeah. You didn't tell me that part.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.83,1:55:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 太棒了\N{\r外文}-Yeah. That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.16,1:55:23.66,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 凱莉 新年快樂 寶寶怎麼樣\N{\r外文}Hi, Kelly. Happy New Year. How's the baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.75,1:55:25.25,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 好大\N{\r外文}-Oh, big.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.54,1:55:27.50,中文,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\r外文}Hi, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.00,1:55:31.04,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂 新年快樂 親愛的\N{\r外文}-Happy New Year. Happy New Year, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.12,1:55:33.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我很高興你能過來 很高興能來這裏\N{\r外文}I'm really happy you're here. Good to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.29,1:55:38.37,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊 霍華德老師和爸爸在一起了\N{\r外文}Oh God, Ms. Howard and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.45,1:55:40.66,中文,,0,0,0,,一直看著你呢 你們倆不許密謀對付我\N{\r外文}-Keeping an eye on you. No plotting against me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.75,1:55:42.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我們會的 你完蛋了 你完了\N{\r外文}Oh, we will. You're toast, you're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.66,1:55:45.33,中文,,0,0,0,,沒這種事 你什麼意思 你完了\N{\r外文}-That's not a thing. ...your point. You're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.41,1:55:47.83,中文,,0,0,0,,他們在為難你 他們發明\N{\r外文}-Giving you a hard time? They're inventing...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.91,1:55:52.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你沒告訴我《美國殭屍 血腥末日》 是你前男友做的\N{\r外文}You didn't tell me that your ex-boyfriend madeAmerican Zombie: Blood Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.20,1:55:56.95,中文,,0,0,0,,那個遊戲太沒創意了 太無聊了 真機靈\N{\r外文}-That game is so unoriginal and boring. Good save.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.04,1:55:59.37,中文,,0,0,0,,玩了36小時後 我就有了這樣的感受\N{\r外文}That's what it felt like after playing it for 36 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.45,1:56:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 大家好\N{\r外文}Okay. Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.16,1:56:06.62,中文,,0,0,0,,聚過來吧 美麗的狂歡者們 來 進來吧\N{\r外文}Hey, gather around, you beautiful revelers. Come on, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.16,1:56:10.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我想敬大家一杯\N{\r外文}I wanted to make a toast. Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.79,1:56:14.70,中文,,0,0,0,,能在這座房子裏團聚 真是太棒了\N{\r外文}It is so incredible to be in this house,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.79,1:56:18.50,中文,,0,0,0,,盧卡斯 亞歷克斯和我 一起在這裏長大\N{\r外文}this house that Lucas and Alex and I grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.58,1:56:21.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你們都知道 今年過得並不輕鬆\N{\r外文}As you all know, this wasn't the easiest year.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.04,1:56:23.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我們經歷了考驗\N{\r外文}It tested us.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.70,1:56:27.12,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 謝謝老朋友們\N{\r外文}So thank you to old friends,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.20,1:56:32.75,中文,,0,0,0,,也謝謝新朋友們 最後 再謝謝我們親愛的母親\N{\r外文}to new friends, and finally, to our lovely dear mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.66,1:56:34.66,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂\N{\r外文}Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.75,1:56:39.04,中文,,0,0,0,,新年快樂 乾杯\N{\r外文}Happy New Year! Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.54,1:56:55.54,中文,,0,0,0,,乾杯\N{\r外文}Cheers.
